(1, 1, '<div>Learning Management System, in short, we can say (LMS). LMS is designed to create, distribute, and manage the delivery of educational content. Also, we can consider the LMS as an eLearning platform. But not all e-Learning platforms are considered LMS.</div><div><br></div><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Mitxen is a WordPress plugin published in the PHP programming language that comes equipped with WordPress. Mitxen WordPress plugin helps students to learn new things or provide training to employees or end-users. With this platform, instructors can create the course, lectures, documents, videos on a particular topic and publish them. Moreover, with this platform, instructors can sell their skills online and build online teaching careers worldwide.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Mitxen is an e-learning management system for WordPress websites. This LMS plugin is created for online instructors. With Mitxen learning management system, an instructor can create different courses on different topics. For example- lectures on accounting, business strategy, communication skills, 3d modeling, cooking, cybersecurity, animals training, drawing, cryptocurrency, leadership, videography, photography, web development, graphic designing, interior designing, etc.</span></p><p><span xss=removed>Mitxen WordPress LMS platform is designed for instructors who want to create and share the courses. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The purpose of Mitxen LMS is to bring instructors and students into one platform where students and instructors get combined to enrich or share knowledge through a structured course-based system. In addition, this LMS platform helps the instructor to create and share attractive courses as well as to earn money.</span></p>', 1),
(2, 2, '<p><span xss=removed>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using \'Content here, content here\', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for \'lorem ipsum\' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).</span></p><p><span xss=removed>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using \'Content here, content here\', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for \'lorem ipsum\' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).</span></p><p><span xss=removed>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using \'Content here, content here\', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for \'lorem ipsum\' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).</span><span xss=removed><br></span><span xss=removed><br></span><br></p>', 1),
(3, 3, '<p><span xss=removed>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using \'Content here, content here\', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for \'lorem ipsum\' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).</span></p><p><span xss=removed>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using \'Content here, content here\', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for \'lorem ipsum\' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).</span><span xss=removed><br></span><br></p>', 1),
(4, 5, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-f3e95719-7fff-357b-cb0a-390cdc52c1ed\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">WordPress plugins are like miniature computational models that extend the functionality of your WordPress site, enabling it to perform more things.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"https://creativeitem.com/v2/uploads/documentation/mitxen-lms/introduction/empty-graphics.png\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"> </span><span xss=\"removed\"><br><span xss=\"removed\">WordPress plugins are designed in the PHP programming language and collaborate with WordPress. WordPress will introduce plugins to your vocabulary; plugins are also an essential element of every WordPress site. WordPress plugin tries to add or enhance the features of your <a href=\"https://creativeitem.com/v2/uploads/documentation/mitxen-lms/introduction/empty-graphics.png\" target=\"_blank\">website</a>.</span></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></span></p><ol><li>Hello world</li><li>Hello world</li><li>Hello world<br></li></ol><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><div><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></div></span>', 1),
(5, NULL, NULL, 0),
(6, 6, '<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Mitxen LMS WordPress plugin tries to give the best user experience to its users. The workflow of Mitxen LMS is friendly and straightforward. All you have to follow the instruction below-</span><span xss=removed><br><br></span></p><ul xss=removed><li dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed role=\"presentation\"><span xss=removed>Installation:</span><span xss=removed> </span><span xss=removed><br></span><span xss=removed>First thing first, you have to download the Mitxen LMS plugin from the codecanyon. Then install the Mitxen plugin on your WordPress site to follow the documentation.</span><span xss=removed><br><br></span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed role=\"presentation\"><span xss=removed>Configuration: </span><span xss=removed><br></span><span xss=removed>After the installation, you have to set up the Mitxen plugin for your site. Then, you have to configure all the basic settings with all applicable data to run this plugin.</span><span xss=removed><br><br></span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed role=\"presentation\"><span xss=removed>Creating the Course:</span><span xss=removed> </span><span xss=removed><br></span><span xss=removed>Now, an instructor is ready to prepare a course or lecture to share after installation and setting up. Instructors can create lessons by providing documents, pictures, and videos according to their expertise. In addition, Mitxen delivers one of the best course editors to make the course more engaging and informative.</span><span xss=removed><br><br></span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed role=\"presentation\"><span xss=removed>Enroll and Sales:</span><span xss=removed> </span><span xss=removed><br></span><span xss=removed>After</span><span xss=removed> </span><span xss=removed>providing</span><span xss=removed> </span><span xss=removed>the course with the help of the Mitxen course editor, an instructor is ready to share his class. After that, students, employees, or end-users can purchase and enroll in the course. When they buy the lecturers, the admin and the instructor start earning money by selling the learners\' approach and growing up a profession.</span><span xss=removed><br><br></span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed role=\"presentation\"><span xss=removed>Learning from the Course:</span><span xss=removed> </span><span xss=removed><br></span><span xss=removed><br></span><span xss=removed>After purchasing the classes, students, employees, or the end-user </span></p></li></ul><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-9e61e43c-7fff-e63a-c1f9-77928ee14419\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>can start learning from the course. With Mitxen LMS, they can get different kinds of unique features. For example- learners get an advanced course player, see course learning progress, save course in wishlist, contact the instructor\'s support. They can also browse the course list by sorting and filtering, secure login, and personal account. Mitxen always provides a friendly user experience efficiently.</span></p>', 1),
(7, 8, 'Hello world', 1),
(8, 7, '<p><span xss=\"removed\">The Ekattor School Management System ERP (Enterprise Resource Planning) is a collection of programs designed to assist schools in administering their executive responsibilities on a day-to-day basis.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p><span xss=\"removed\">In the 21st century, almost every well-known educational institute uses a school management system to enhance ability and productivity. This school management system empowers schools to keep track of their daily operations while centralizing their resources and information. This managing system helps to reduce the pressure of managing a large amount of data from the school.&nbsp;</span><br></p><div><br></div><div><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Who is Ekattor for?</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Ekattor school management system ERP is an online platform where authorities can operate daily activities and control school data.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Student admissions, Student management, Admin management, Permission attributing, Exam management, Fees management, Accounting management, Library management, Teacher management, Parents management are included in the routine activities. Ekattor school management system ERP is helpful for:&nbsp;</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Schools&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Colleges&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Universities&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Other educational institutions etc.</span></li></ul></div>', 1),
(9, 9, '<ul xss=removed><li>Apache server for running php</li><li>PHP version 7</li><li>Mysql database access, purchase code during installation</li><li>Php curl should be enabled</li><li>One purchase code is legal for using one domain only</li></ul>', 1),
(10, 10, '<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Please follow the below steps to complete the installation process.</span></p><ul><li><span xss=\"removed\">After purchasing Ekattor, you will get the application as a zip file. Upload​ ​that​ ​zip​ ​file​ ​on ​your​ ​server.</span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-71bd3c4e-7fff-4279-d428-0710155e64a9\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b91d48f1-7fff-cef9-a7e5-219ae496b5de\"><span xss=\"removed\">You​ ​can​ ​upload​ ​anywhere​ ​inside​ ​your​ </span><span xss=\"removed\">​public_html</span><span xss=\"removed\">​ ​folder​ ​or​ ​any​ ​sub-folder you​ ​want. ​Just​ ​keep​ ​in​ ​mind​ ​the​ ​directory name​ ​where​ ​you​ ​have​ ​uploaded​ ​it.</span></span></span></span></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">Unzip​ ​the​ ​file.</span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-71bd3c4e-7fff-4279-d428-0710155e64a9\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b91d48f1-7fff-cef9-a7e5-219ae496b5de\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-047f5850-7fff-e6d9-5b47-fa8f97828f60\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-9e3fb7fd-7fff-0c0e-540e-32de1c29d92b\"><span xss=\"removed\">Go​ ​to​ ​your​ ​preferred​ ​web​ ​browser​ ​and​ ​type​ ​the​ ​url​ ​where​ ​you​ ​have unzipped​ ​the​ ​file.​ For​ ​example​ ​-​ ​if​ ​you​ ​have​ ​a​ ​domain​ example.com​ ​and​ ​you have​ ​unzipped​ ​the​ ​files​ ​inside​ ​a​ ​folder​ ekattor,​ ​the​ ​url​ ​will​ ​be </span><span xss=\"removed\">example.com/ekattor.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li><li><span xss=\"removed\">After​ ​you​ ​have​ ​entered​ ​the​ ​url​ ​on​ ​your​ ​browser​ ​will​ ​see​ ​the​ ​screen​ ​below.</span><img src=\"https://creativeitem.com/v2/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/getting-started-with-ekattor-erp/step-0.png\" xss=\"removed\"></li><li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad09b553-7fff-39aa-1067-98aae881bc9a\">This is the first step of the installation. Before starting the installation process, you will need to have CodeCanyon purchase code, the database name, database username, database password and database host. You can get the purchase code from your purchase information on codecanyon, for having the database information, you will need to create a new database on your server.</span></li><li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad09b553-7fff-39aa-1067-98aae881bc9a\">After you hit the ‘Start Installation Process’ button you will see the screen below.</span><img src=\"https://creativeitem.com/v2/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/getting-started-with-ekattor-erp/step-1.png\" xss=\"removed\"></li><li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad09b553-7fff-39aa-1067-98aae881bc9a\">This screen checks if the required files have the write permission and curl is enabled or not. If these are not enabled, you will face issues in the installation process. So make sure that all the three points on that screen have a green check mark. If everything is fine and you hit the ‘Go To Next Step’ button will be presented with this screen.</span><img src=\"https://creativeitem.com/v2/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/getting-started-with-ekattor-erp/step-2.png\" xss=\"removed\"></li><li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad09b553-7fff-39aa-1067-98aae881bc9a\">Here you will need to insert your purchase code that you have got from CodeCanyon and hit the ‘Continue’ button which will lead you to the screen below.</span><img src=\"https://creativeitem.com/v2/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/getting-started-with-ekattor-erp/step-3.png\" xss=\"removed\"></li><li dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\" role=\"presentation\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-62438f3d-7fff-ee6a-4e2d-e7b6f83f139c\" xss=\"removed\">Here you will need to provide the database credentials, which you have created for this application. The installer will check if the information are correct after you hit the ‘Continue’ button and if everything is fine, you will be directed to the page below.</span><img src=\"https://creativeitem.com/v2/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/getting-started-with-ekattor-erp/step-4.png\" xss=removed></p></li></ul><ul><li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad09b553-7fff-39aa-1067-98aae881bc9a\">Now all you have to do is hit the ‘Install’ button which will automatically import the database of the application to your created database. Please wait while the import operation is being done. This may take a while according to your server performance.</span></li><li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad09b553-7fff-39aa-1067-98aae881bc9a\">After the installer has successfully imported the database, you will get the following page.</span><img src=\"https://creativeitem.com/v2/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/getting-started-with-ekattor-erp/step-5.png\" xss=removed></li><li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad09b553-7fff-39aa-1067-98aae881bc9a\">Fill up the information required and hit the button ‘Set me up’. This will save your school name and administrator login credentials which will be required later for logging in into the application and will present the following page.</span><img src=\"https://creativeitem.com/v2/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/getting-started-with-ekattor-erp/step-6.png\" xss=removed></li><li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad09b553-7fff-39aa-1067-98aae881bc9a\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0652557f-7fff-8292-fe7c-22bfb69b997f\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3fe1f18a-7fff-af89-42e0-fef333d3acb7\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-49b41333-7fff-e0e1-404d-266f784f543a\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e55514cd-7fff-084a-eaae-7bd03bcff653\"><span xss=\"removed\">Now hit the ‘Log In’ button which will redirect you to the backend of the application where you will be able to login as Super administrator using the email and password you have entered in the previous step. </span><span xss=\"removed\"> INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(42, 45, '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c9a51c3e-7fff-582d-1fd8-e37358fd29c0\"><span xss=\"removed\">Mastery </span><span xss=\"removed\">is an online subscription-based LMS software. In </span><span xss=\"removed\">Mastery </span><span xss=\"removed\">LMS, Admin or teacher creates the class on a particular topic and makes it published for the users, helping students learn things or providing training to employees or any students.</span></span></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">What Mastery LMS does?</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Mastery LMS operates on a subscription system every Month/Year/Number of days. By purchasing a subscription package to this LMS, the users can access all classes of the site. It will make your website more attractive and greatly help users to keep up.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can create free classes and individually free lessons by Mastery. The lesson playing page is very user-friendly at Mastery. Students can discuss their problems with others, add class reviews, and follow the instructor at the same place.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">What are the benefits of Mastery LMS?</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Mastery runs on a subscription system every Month/Year/Number of days. By purchasing a subscription package to Mastery, the users can access all classes of the site.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Which will make your website more attractive and greatly help users to keep up. Also, you can create free classes and individually free lessons by Mastery. The lesson playing page is great at Mastery, where students can discuss their problems with others, add class reviews, and follow the teacher at the same place.</span></p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c9a51c3e-7fff-582d-1fd8-e37358fd29c0\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></span><br></p>', 1),
(43, 46, '<p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">First, download the source code of </span><span xss=\"removed\">Mastery</span><span xss=\"removed\">, then upload the application on your server and install it following our Installation documentation.</span></p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c465a89b-7fff-b2ab-8819-3894894eadd8\"><br><span xss=\"removed\">Configure some basic information from the settings to prepare the </span><span xss=\"removed\">Mastery </span><span xss=\"removed\">to create the class. You can create the classes after configuring the settings. Also, you can create the classes from a teacher panel.</span></span><br></p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-966cd086-7fff-d805-2d63-18c39d9f8feb\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></span><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Install</span></h3></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">We have followed a type of automation process to install the Mastery. Which you easily complete the installation process with zero coding knowledge.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Free &amp; Premium class</span></h3><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The method of adding classes to Mastery is very flexible, where you can add classes as sliders, featured, recommended, and free classes. You can also add multiple tags or skills to the classes, which will help the students to find their classes.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Subscription</span></h3><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Monthly / Yearly / Number of days you can use these three types of packages on Mastery and the packages active/deactivate as yours needs.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Class</span></h3><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The method of adding classes to </span><span xss=\"removed\">Mastery </span><span xss=\"removed\">is very flexible, where you can add classes as sliders, featured, recommended, and free classes. You can also add multiple </span><span xss=\"removed\">tags </span><span xss=\"removed\">or </span><span xss=\"removed\">skills </span><span xss=\"removed\">to the classes, which will help the students to find their classes.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Review &amp; discussion</span></h3><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Allows students who have purchased subscription packages to add class reviews and discuss their problems on the site. Which is a great feature for an LMS system.</span></p>', 1),
(44, 47, '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-4c73b3e9-7fff-7cc4-e5e6-c00937479011\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Mastery</span><span xss=\"removed\"> runs on a subscription system every </span><span xss=\"removed\">Month </span><span xss=\"removed\">/ </span><span xss=\"removed\">Year </span><span xss=\"removed\">/ </span><span xss=\"removed\">Number of days</span><span xss=\"removed\">. By purchasing a subscription package to </span><span xss=\"removed\">Mastery</span><span xss=\"removed\">, the users can access all classes of the site. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Which will make your website more attractive and greatly help users to keep up. Also, you can create free classes and individually free lessons by </span><span xss=\"removed\">Mastery</span><span xss=\"removed\">. The lesson playing page is great at </span><span xss=\"removed\">Mastery</span><span xss=\"removed\">, where students can discuss their problems with others, add class reviews, and follow the teacher at the same place.</span></p>', 1),
