(52, 61, '<h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Home page</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-frontend-homepage.png\" title=\"Academy Frontend Homepage\" alt=\"Academy Frontend Homepage\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Frontend Homepage\" alt=\"Academy Frontend Homepage\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Figure 1. <span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Frontend Homepage</span></span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Users may access the majority of the view pages without logging in. When users access the Academy LMS application for the first time without signup, they will see the Course Search option on the home page and see the top courses and the top 10 latest courses.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Course categories menu</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-frontend-Course-categories-menu.png\" title=\"Academy Frontend Course Categories Menu\" alt=\"Academy Frontend Course Categories Menu\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Frontend Course Categories Menu\" alt=\"Academy Frontend Course Categories Menu\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Figure 2.</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><b>&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Frontend Course Category Menu</span></span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">On the left side of the home page, a course menu with a drop-down menu includes categories and subcategories. Category and subcategory Select a specific category. Can view all courses in the department at once.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Course Search bar</span></h3><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\"><br></span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-frontend-search-bar.png\" title=\"Academy Frontend Search Bar\" alt=\"Academy Frontend Search Bar\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Frontend Search Bar\" alt=\"Academy Frontend Search Bar\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; text-align: inherit; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><b>Figure 3.</b></span><b style=\"background-color: transparent; text-align: inherit; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"> </b><span style=\"background-color: transparent; text-align: inherit; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Academy LMS Frontend search bar</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; text-align: inherit; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Users can find a course using the search box above. Can use the search bar to locate the required courses.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Cart page</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-frontend-shopping-cart.png\" title=\"Academy Frontend Shopping Cart\" alt=\"Academy Frontend Shopping Cart\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Frontend Shopping Cart\" alt=\"Academy Frontend Shopping Cart\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Figure 4.</span><strong xss=\"removed\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"> </strong><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Frontend Shopping Cart</span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">When users add their favorite courses to their add to cart, the cart page displays all the courses added to their add to cart.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Sign Up page</span></span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-sign-up-page.png\" title=\"Academy Sign Up Page\" alt=\"Academy Sign Up Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Sign Up Page\" alt=\"Academy Sign Up Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><b><br></b></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Figure 5.</span><b style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"> </b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Sign up page&nbsp;</span></h5><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></h5><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Login page</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-login-page.png\" title=\"Academy Login Page\" alt=\"Academy Login Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Login Page\" alt=\"Academy Login Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Figure 6.</span><strong xss=\"removed\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"> </strong><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Log in Page</span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">There are two buttons on the right side of the home page. t</span><span xss=\"removed\">he first is to log in. The second is to sign up. If a user already has an account, they do not need to sign up again. Users can purchase the course if they have an account.</span></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Top courses</span></span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-top-courses.png\" title=\"Academy Top Courses\" alt=\"Academy Top Courses\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Top Courses\" alt=\"Academy Top Courses\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><b xss=\"removed\"><br></b></span></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 7.<b>&nbsp;</b></span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Academy LMS Top Course</span></span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">On the home page are featured top courses. Users quickly find suitable courses.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 1.5rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>Top 10 Latest courses</b></span><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-top-10-latest-courses.png\" title=\"Academy Top 10 Latest Courses\" alt=\"Academy Top 10 Latest Courses\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Top 10 Latest Courses\" alt=\"Academy Top 10 Latest Courses\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 8.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Latest Course</span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The top 10 latest courses the added to the homepage. Users can select the most recent courses and purchases by signing up.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Course filter page</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-course-filter-page.png\" title=\"Academy Course Filter Page\" alt=\"Academy Course Filter Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Course Filter Page\" alt=\"Academy Course Filter Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 9.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Academy LMS Course Filter Page</span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Users can filter Categories, Price, Level, Language, usage courses before signing up to Academy LMS and purchasing courses.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Course List view</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-course-list-view.png\" title=\"Academy Course List View\" alt=\"Academy Course List View\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Course List View\" alt=\"Academy Course List View\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 10.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Course List View</span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">If the user wants to see all the courses on the course page in a list, they can see it using the list-icon at the top.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Course grid view</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-course-grid-view.png\" title=\"Academy Course Grid View\" alt=\"Academy Course Grid View\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Course Grid View\" alt=\"Academy Course Grid View\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 11.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Academy LMS Course Grid&nbsp;</span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">If users want to see all the courses on the course page in a grid, they can see it using the grid icon above.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Course details page</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-course-details-page.png\" title=\"Academy Course Details Page\" alt=\"Academy Course Details Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Course Details Page\" alt=\"Academy Course Details Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 12.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Academy LMS Course Details Page</span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">A user can view the course details page. Course ratings, curriculum, course requirements, course description, course previews, and can learn about the instructor without signing up.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">About page</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-about-page.png\" title=\"Academy About Page\" alt=\"Academy About Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy About Page\" alt=\"Academy About Page\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 13.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Academy LMS About Page</span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The user can learn about the Academy LMS application without signing up by visiting the \'about page\' in the menu below.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Refund policy</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-refundpolicy.png\" title=\"Academy Refundpolicy\" alt=\"Academy Refundpolicy\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Refundpolicy\" alt=\"Academy Refundpolicy\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 14.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Refund Policy</span>&nbsp;</span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Users may learn about the Academy LMS application\'s refund policy without signing up by visiting the \'Refund policy page\' in the footer menu.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Privacy policy page</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-privacy-policy.png\" title=\"Academy Privacy Policy\" alt=\"Academy Privacy Policy\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Privacy Policy\" alt=\"Academy Privacy Policy\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 15.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Academy LMS Frontend Privacy Policy&nbsp;</span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The user can check the Academy LMS application\'s privacy policy without signing up by visiting the \'privacy policy page\' in the menu below.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Terms and condition page&nbsp;</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-terms-&amp;-condition.png\" title=\"Academy Terms &amp; Condition\" alt=\"Academy Terms &amp; Condition\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Terms &amp; Condition\" alt=\"Academy Terms &amp; Condition\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 16.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Frontend Terms and Conditions&nbsp;</span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Users will be able to visit the Terms and Conditions page without signing up.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Language Change section</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-language-change.png\" title=\"Academy Language Change\" alt=\"Academy Language Change\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Language Change\" alt=\"Academy Language Change\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Figure 17.</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Academy LMS Frontend Language Change</span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Users can also change the language of the website to their chosen one.</span></p>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(53, 62, '<p></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Dashboard</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-dashboard.png\" title=\"Academy Dashboard\" alt=\"Academy Dashboard\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Dashboard\" alt=\"Academy Dashboard\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Dashboard</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">All required numbers that need viewing more often are displayed on the dashboard. Such as income from the total number of courses, lessons, enrollment, and the most recent payout withdrawal request, etc.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Manage Course</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-manage-courses.png\" title=\"Academy Manage Courses\" alt=\"Academy Manage Courses\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Manage Courses\" alt=\"Academy Manage Courses\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><b>Figure 2.</b></span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><b>&nbsp;</b>Academy LMS Course manager</span></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The administrator manages all courses. Approves pending instructor courses and sells own courses direct.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Add new Course</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-add-new-course.png\" title=\"Academy Add New Course\" alt=\"Academy Add New Course\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Add New Course\" alt=\"Academy Add New Course\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Figure 3.</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><b>&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS adding course form</span></span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Before creating a course, the administrator must first create a section. Go to the course menu on the Admin left to complete a new course. It is possible to add a new course.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Course category</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-course-category.png\" title=\"Academy Course Category\" alt=\"Academy Course Category\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Course Category\" alt=\"Academy Course Category\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Figure 4.</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Course Category Page</span></span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Course categories can organize very quickly with unlimited top categories and subcategories.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Coupons</span></h3><h5><br></h5><h5><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-coupons.png\" title=\"Academy Coupons\" alt=\"