S Private Messaging&nbsp;</span></span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Admin can communicate with all students and instructors using the academy LMS internal messaging system.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Addons</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-addons.png\" title=\"Academy Addons\" alt=\"Academy Addons\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Addons\" alt=\"Academy Addons\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 20.</span></strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Addons</span></span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Academy supports several add-ons. The admin can only install those add-ons.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Themes</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-themes.png\" title=\"Academy Themes\" alt=\"Academy Themes\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Themes\" alt=\"Academy Themes\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; font-size: 0.9375rem; text-align: inherit; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 21.</span></strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"background: transparent; font-size: 0.9375rem; text-align: inherit; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;Academy LMS Themes</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"background: transparent; font-size: 0.9375rem; text-align: inherit; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Academy LMS supports multiple themes.&nbsp;</span><span xss=\"removed\">Admin can install these, and he can also switch to different themes.</span></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">System settings</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-system-settings.png\" title=\"Academy System Settings\" alt=\"Academy S