-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The admin can set up the multi-language from the Academy LMS&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Smtp settings</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-smtp.png\" title=\"Academy Smtp\" alt=\"Academy Smtp\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Smtp\" alt=\"Academy Smtp\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 26.</span></strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS SMTP Settings Page</span></span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Admin can change the academy LMS SMTP settings.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Social login</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-social-link.png\" title=\"Academy Social Link\" alt=\"Academy Social Link\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy Social Link\" alt=\"Academy Social Link\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 27.</span></strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Social Login Page</span></span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Suppose the admin has set up social login. Users can log in to the academy using their Facebook accounts.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">About this application</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/getting-started/academy-about.png\" title=\"Academy About\" alt=\"Academy About\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Academy About\" alt=\"Academy About\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"></strong></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 28.</span></strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS About the Application</span></span></span></h5><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Admin can see about the academy LMS application.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Manage profile</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">He also has a profile manager section to update his data and password as a user.</span></p>', 1),
(54, 104, '<p><span xss=\"removed\">﻿</span><font face=\"Arial\">Ekattor ERP  provides the best user experience. This school management system is decorated to help seven kinds of users. They are-</font></p><ul><li><font face=\"Arial\">Superadmin</font></li><li><font face=\"Arial\">Admin</font></li><li><font face=\"Arial\">Teacher</font></li><li><font face=\"Arial\">Parent</font></li><li><font face=\"Arial\">Student</font></li><li><font face=\"Arial\">Accountant</font></li><li><font face=\"Arial\">Librarian<br><br></font></li></ul><p><font face=\"Arial\">In Ekattor, every user has to play different roles with different permissions to operate the daily activities of an educational institution. This permission helps the users to control and run the institute smoothly.</font></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Superadmin:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">A superadmin has to play the most crucial role. He has the highest number of privileges and permissions. Mostly, he can add, edit, and remove school admin. He can monitor and control academic activities, live classes, exam-related activities, accounting-related activities, back-office-related activities, and online courses.</p><div><br></div><h4><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Admin:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">An admin has the highest permissions and privileges after superadmin. An admin can monitor, control, and take action on academics, examinations, live classes, accounting, and back-office-related activities. But for a particular institute. </p><div><br></div><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Teacher:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">A teacher\'s role is orienting on teaching and academic-related activities. He has permission to overview the list of students, class routine, subjects, event calendar, and back-office activities. He can overview, edit, and delete student\'s and their parent\'s information. A teacher has permission to issue ID cards for students, and he can take attendance/biometric attendance. He has the authorization to create the syllabus, add or edit new live classes, provide marks and comments on the examination.</p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\">In Ekattor, a teacher can add assignments, publish, draft, expire, make questions and review them, and he can also create and modify online courses here.</p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Parent:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">In Ekattor, a parent can overview the teacher\'s list, academic (daily attendance, class routine, syllabus, and event calendar), and back-office activities. Parents can also monitor the exam marks and grades. They can make payments for their children./ They can pay fees for their children in this panel.</p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Student:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">A student has the permission to overview the list of teachers, daily attendance, class routine, syllabus, event calendar, back-office, exam marks, and grades in Ekattor. A student can overview marks, comments and submit their assignment. They can also join live classes, pay feeses, issue books from the library, watch online courses and get specific course information from here.</p><div><br></div><h4><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Accountant:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">In this panel, an accountant gets all the permission about financial activities. An accountant has permission to add, edit and delete expense and expense categories. They can add mass or single invoices, export reports in CSV, PDF, and Print. </p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Librarian:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">A librarian has track of every book in the library, and they will get all library-related activities permissions. They also have permission to issue books, and they can add, edit, and remove books from the library and have permission to issue books.<br></p>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(55, 105, '<p xss=\"removed\">The academic activities of an educational institute help to operate classes and other education-related activities. In this panel, we will discuss with you about academic terms of the Ekattor school management system.</p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Attendance:</span></span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">In this school management system, superadmin, admin, and teacher can take student\'s attendance to track academic progress. They can also take biometric attendance by adding additional add-ons, and students and parents can overview attendance from their panel. </p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Class routine:</span></span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">The class routine is another part of academic terms in Ekattor. The superadmin and admin create the class routine for different classes. In this panel, class routine helps to complete regular academic activities. Students and parents can watch class routines to maintain everyday educational activities.<br><br></p><h4>Subject:</h4><p>In this school system management, the subject is a part of academic activities. Students, teachers, and parents have permission to overview subjects. Only superadmin and admin can add different subjects for different classes.<br></p><p></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\">Syllabus:</span></h4><p></p><p xss=\"removed\">The syllabus is another essential part of academic activities in Ekattor. The syllabus supports other educational activities, such as class routine, subject, and department. In this panel, superadmin, admin, and teacher have permission to create the syllabus for the students, and only parents and students have permission to view the syllabus.</p><div><br></div><h4><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Class:</span></span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">In this term, superadmin and admin can create a class to operate other\'s regular academic activities. They can also create sections, edit, and delete if they need. Classes and sections help to run class routine, subject, syllabus, classroom, and department.<br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\">Classroom:</span></h4>The classroom is a significant part to operate academic activities in an educational institute. Only admin and superadmin can add, edit and remove classrooms, and they have an essential role in making a proper layout for the institute.<br><p></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><h4><span xss=\"removed\">Department:</span></h4><p></p><p xss=\"removed\">Every educational institute has different departments to function academic progress. In Ekattor, superadmin and admin have the authority to add, edit, and erase various departments.</p><div><br></div><h4><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Event calendar:</span></span></h4><p xss=\"removed\">The academic calendar is an essential part of this term. It helps to make track of an academic session. Everyone can see the event and detail from this panel. In Ekattor, superadmin and admin can add an event on the academic calendar. Also, they can edit and delete any occurrence from the calendar. Teachers, parents, and students can view this academic calendar from their panel.<br></p>', 1),
(56, 106, '<p>The examination is a great way to evaluate what the students have learned concerning particular subjects, and it shows the path of learning. This exam system has an essential role in the process of education and the entire educational institute. There are few things in the examination system. They are -</p><ul><li>Marks</li><li>Exams</li><li>Grades</li><li>Promotions</li></ul><h4 xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Marks:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Mark is a score in the form of a number, percentage, or letter that a teacher gives a student\'s in the examination. In Ekattor, superadmin, admin, and teacher can provide marks, add comments and take action on marks. Parents and students have the authority to overview marks from their accounts.<br><br></span></p><h4 xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Exams:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this school management system, superadmin and admin can add new exams. Also, they can update exam name, starting date, ending date, and erase exam. Teachers, parents, and students can watch this panel.<br><br></span></p><h4 xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Grades:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"></p><p></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Only grades can define a student\'s marks in the examination. Superadmin and admin can add new grades, points, and ranges. Only students and parents have permission to overview the grades in Ekattor.<br><br></span></p><h4 xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Promotions:</span></h4><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After completing a session in an educational institute, students get a promotion to enroll next session. It\'s a part of the examination system, and a student has to achieve suitable marks to get the promotion. In Ekattor, only superadmin and admin can enroll in a new session or promote a student.</span></p>', 1),
(57, 114, '<p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" xss=\"removed\">In Ekattor, only superadmin and admin can control and overview student\'s information and activities. For this, you have to follow the following steps&nbsp;</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Users</strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" xss=\"removed\">&gt;</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Student</strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" xss=\"removed\">.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After opening the student\'s form, you have to select the class and section. Then you have to press the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Filter</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/filter-student.png\" title=\"Filter Student\" alt=\"Filter Student\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Filter Student\" alt=\"Filter Student\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Filtering Option</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After opening the student\'s list, you can overview:&nbsp;</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Student\'s code</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Student\'s name</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Student\'s image</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">,\" you can monitor student\'s profiles, edit information, and delete students.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/introducing-students-option.png\" title=\"Introducing Students Option\" alt=\"Introducing Students Option\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Students Option\" alt=\"Introducing Students Option\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Managing Students</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Profile</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button. You can overview student\'s and their parent\'s information here.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/students-information.png\" title=\"Students Information\" alt=\"Students Information\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Students Information\" alt=\"Students Information\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Student Information</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br>And<br><br></span><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/parent-information.png\" title=\"Parent Information\" alt=\"Parent Information\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Parent Information\" alt=\"Parent Information\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Student\'s Parent Information</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also edit and update student\'s information. For this, you have to select \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Edit</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" You can change students:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Name</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Email</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Parent</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Section</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Birthdate</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Blood group</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Gender</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Address</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Phone</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Profile image</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After providing all information, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update students information</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/updating-student-information.png\" title=\"Updating Student Information\" alt=\"Updating Student Information\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Student Information\" alt=\"Updating Student Information\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 5.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Students Information</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To delete a student\'s account, you must select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Delete</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Continue</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to confirm your action.</span></p>', 1),
(58, 115, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Ekattor, only superadmin and admin can add new students to the school. As a superadmin or admin, you can enroll students in three ways. They are:</span></p><ol style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Single admission</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Bulk admission</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Excel upload</span></li></ol><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To enroll new students, you have to follow the steps below:&nbsp;</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the user panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\">Select the \"<b>User</b>\" option from the left menu.</li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Admission</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Single student admission</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the required information.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add student</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your data.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/single-student-admission.png\" title=\"Single Student Admission\" alt=\"Single Student Admission\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Single Student Admission\" alt=\"Single Student Admission\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Single Student Admission</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Ekattor, you can enroll more than one student at a time. For this, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the user panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\">Select the \"<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">User</span>\" option from the left menu.</li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Admission</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Bulk student admission</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">+</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option to add more students to your list.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To remove students, select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">x</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">For confirmation, select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add student</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/bulk-student-adamission.png\" title=\"Bulk Student Adamission\" alt=\"Bulk Student Adamission\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Bulk Student Adamission\" alt=\"Bulk Student Adamission\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Bulk Student Admission</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can upload an excel file to admit students to this school management system. To upload an excel file, follow the simple steps below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the user panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\">Select the \"<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">User</span>\" option from the left menu.</li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Admission</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Excel upload</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose a class and section.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Generate or upload a CSV file from your device.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"<b>Add student</b>\" button to save your data.&nbsp;</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/excel-student-admission.png\" title=\"Excel Student Admission\" alt=\"Excel Student Admission\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Excel Student Admission\" alt=\"Excel Student Admission\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Excel Upload</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br>That\'s it!</span></p>', 1),
(59, 116, '<p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Admin has to play the most crucial role after superadmin in Ekattor, and the only superadmin can select an admin for a particular school.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><font color=\"#0e101a\">To manage and control admins from the superadmin panel, you have to navigate:</font><br></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the superadmin menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">User</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Admin</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/introducing-admin..png\" title=\"Introducing Admin.\" alt=\"Introducing Admin.\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Admin.\" alt=\"Introducing Admin.\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Managing Admin</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After opening the admin list, you can create, update, or delete admins from the application.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To create a new admin, you have to click the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Create admin\"&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">button from the admin list.</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></strong></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/adding-admin.png\" title=\"Adding Admin\" alt=\"Adding Admin\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Adding Admin\" alt=\"Adding Admin\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Creating New Admin</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, you have to provide:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Admin\'s name</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Email</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Password</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Phone number</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">School name</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Gander</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Blood group</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Address</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Providing all required information, select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Create admin</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your data.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/creating-admin.png\" title=\"Creating Admin\" alt=\"Creating Admin\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Creating Admin\" alt=\"Creating Admin\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Saving New Admin\'s Information</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">As a superadmin, you can modify and update the admin\'s information. For this, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Option</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from the admin list.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Edit</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Change the required information.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update admin</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option for confirmation.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/updating-admin.png\" title=\"Updating Admin\" alt=\"Updating Admin\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Admin\" alt=\"Updating Admin\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating admin\'s information</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To remove an admin from your application, you have to select the \"</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">Delete</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from the \"</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">Option</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button. Now, select the \"</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">Continue</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to confirm your action.</span><br></p>', 1);
