rgin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Address</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">About&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Profile photo</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, you have to select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Create teacher</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your data.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/creating-teacher-part-one.png\" title=\"Creating Teacher Part One\" alt=\"Creating Teacher Part One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Creating Teacher Part One\" alt=\"Creating Teacher Part One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/creating-teacher-part-two.png\" title=\"Creating Teacher Part Two\" alt=\"Creating Teacher Part Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Creating Teacher Part Two\" alt=\"Creating Teacher Part Two\" style=\"max-