le=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Accountant\" alt=\"Updating Accountant\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Accountant\'s Information</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To remove an accountant,&nbsp; you have to choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Delete</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" and select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Continue</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button for confirmation.</span><br></p>', 1);
