rver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Saving New Subject\'s Information</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To overview, edit, and delete a subject, you have to select a class and press the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Filter</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/academic/filter-subject.png\" title=\"Filter Subject\" alt=\"Filter Subject\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Filter Subject\" alt=\"Filter Subject\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Filtering Subject</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To update the subject, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Edit</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" Now, you can change the class and subject. To finalize your updated information, click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update subject</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/academic/updating-subject.png\" title=\"Updating Subject\" alt=\"Updating Subject\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Subject\" alt=\"Updating Subject\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Subject</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To delete a subject from the application, you have to select the \"</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">Delete</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-space