 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After opening the department creation form, you have to provide a new department name and click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Create department</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/academic/creating-department.png\" title=\"Creating Department\" alt=\"Creating Department\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Creating Department\" alt=\"Creating Department\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Saving New Department\'s Data</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To edit and update the department, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transpar