=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also pay your unpaid fees in this application Online. To complete your fees, you have to follow the steps:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;Select an unpaid transaction.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Make payment</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Option</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select a suitable payment gateway and complete the transaction.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the required account information of your payment gateway.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/accounting-ekattor/make-payment.png\" title=\"Make Payment\" alt=\"Make Payment\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Make Payment\" alt=\"Make Payment\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Payment Gateway</span></span></h5>', 1),
(85, 141, '<p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Ekattor, superadmin, admin and accountant can access the accounting sector. In this accountant panel, you can overview the number of total students, teachers, parents, staff, students invoice list, daily attendance, event list, expense list, and so on.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/accounting-ekattor/introducing-accountant-panel.png\" title=\"Introducing Accountant Panel\" alt=\"Introducing Accountant Panel\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Accountant Panel\" alt=\"Introducing Accountant Panel\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Accountant Panel</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, an accountant can create, edit, delete and print out student\'s fees in the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Student fee manager</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel.</span></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/accounting-ekattor/accountant-student-fee-manager.png\" title=\"Accountant Student Fee Manager\" alt=\"Accountant Student Fee Manager\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Accountant Student Fee Manager\" alt=\"Accountant Student Fee Manager\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Student\'s Fee Manager (Accountant Panel)</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Also, you can add, update and delete the expense and its category in the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Accounting</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(86, 146, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">As a superadmin, you have full access to the settings option in Ekattor ERP. Here you can update your school management system, modify settings, change the logo. For this, you have to navigate:&nbsp;</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the superadmin panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"<b>Settings</b>\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"<b>System settings</b>\" from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/introducing-system-settings-part-one.png\" title=\"Introducing System Settings Part One\" alt=\"Introducing System Settings Part One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing System Settings Part One\" alt=\"Introducing System Settings Part One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/introducing-system-settings-part-two.png\" title=\"Introducing System Settings Part Two\" alt=\"Introducing System Settings Part Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing System Settings Part Two\" alt=\"Introducing System Settings Part Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP System Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\">In this panel, you can update:</span><br></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The system name</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The system title</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">School email</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">School phone number</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Fax</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Address</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Purchase code</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Time zone</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Footer text</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Footer link</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Youtube API key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Vimeo API key</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After providing all information, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update system</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button for confirmation.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/updating-settings.png\" title=\"Updating Settings\" alt=\"Updating Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Settings\" alt=\"Updating Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Update System Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also update Ekattor for a better user experience. For this, you have to select the update file from your device and click the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/updating-product.png\" title=\"Updating Product\" alt=\"Updating Product\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Product\" alt=\"Updating Product\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Application</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br>In this panel, you can change the system logo. You can upload the logo from your device and select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update logo</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/updating-logo.png\" title=\"Updating Logo\" alt=\"Updating Logo\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Logo\" alt=\"Updating Logo\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Application Logo&nbsp;</span></span></h5>', 1);
