(87, 147, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">A superadmin can modify and update the website in this school management system. As a superadmin, you have to follow the steps:&nbsp;</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the superadmin panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Website settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/introducing-website-setting-part-one.png\" title=\"Introducing Website Setting Part One\" alt=\"Introducing Website Setting Part One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Website Setting Part One\" alt=\"Introducing Website Setting Part One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/introducing-website-setting-part-two.png\" title=\"Introducing Website Setting Part Two\" alt=\"Introducing Website Setting Part Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Website Setting Part Two\" alt=\"Introducing Website Setting Part Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-041f131e-7fff-9fe4-3e9a-7fc4470bbea3\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></span></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Website Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><h3><span xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">General Settings:</span></span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can update the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">General settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" In this settings panel, you can edit:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Website title</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Social links. Like: Facebook, Twitter, Youtube, Linkedin, Gmail, Instagram.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Home page note title</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Home page note description</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Copyright text</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Header logo</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Footer logo</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option to complete your action.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/updating-general-settings-part-one.png\" title=\"Updating General Settings Part One\" alt=\"Updating General Settings Part One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating General Settings Part One\" alt=\"Updating General Settings Part One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/updating-general-settings-part-two.png\" title=\"Updating General Settings Part Two\" alt=\"Updating General Settings Part Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating General Settings Part Two\" alt=\"Updating General Settings Part Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ad8d867a-7fff-858a-ae9e-53b815840e4f\"></span></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Events:</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also manage events from this panel. To monitor and control this panel, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the superadmin panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Website settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Events</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/intrroducing-event.png\" title=\"Intrroducing Event\" alt=\"Intrroducing Event\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Intrroducing Event\" alt=\"Intrroducing Event\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Event Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To add new events, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Create event</str