(89, 149, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Superadmin can access the payment settings option. In this panel, you can manage the payment system of your school application. For this, you have to follow the steps:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the superadmin panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to the \"Settings\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"Payment settings\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/introducing-payment-settings.png\" title=\"Introducing Payment Settings\" alt=\"Introducing Payment Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Payment Settings\" alt=\"Introducing Payment Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Payment Settings</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this settings panel, you can update:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Preferred currency.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Currency position.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, you have to select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update system currency</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your settings.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/updating-system-currency.png\" title=\"Updating System Currency\" alt=\"Updating System Currency\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating System Currency\" alt=\"Updating System Currency\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></em></strong></p><p xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></em></strong></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating System Currency</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Note:</em></strong><em style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;Make sure that your \"</em><strong style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">System currency</em></strong><em style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" and other gateway currency are the same.</em><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">PayPal settings:</span></h3></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also update and change the PayPal account information in the\"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Payment settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel. You can change:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Activation status</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Currency</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Mode</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Client id (Sandbox)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Client id (Production)</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After providing the information, click the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update PayPal settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" to confirm your update.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/updating-PayPal-settings.png\" title=\"Updating PayPal Settings\" alt=\"Updating PayPal Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating PayPal Settings\" alt=\"Updating PayPal Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating PayPal Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To get the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Client ID</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" and \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Secret key</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" for your PayPal account, you have to follow the steps below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Navigate to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">PayPal Developers Website</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" home page.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the dashboard.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also log in with your mobile number using&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">OTP</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set up the profile.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Your Name</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Dashboard</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" in the top right corner.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Create App</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" to create a new app.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the details for the new app.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now you can see the PayPal Client Id and secret.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Stripe Settings:</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, you can also update the Stripe account in the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Payment settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel. You can update:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Activation status</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Currency</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Test mode</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Test secret key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Test public key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Live secret key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Live public key</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update stripe settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" to save your information.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/stripe-ekattor.png\" title=\"Stripe Ekattor\" alt=\"Stripe Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Stripe Ekattor\" alt=\"Stripe Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 