server-spaces=\"true\">Toggle the option that says \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Viewing test data</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Viewing live data</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Reveal live key token</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now you can see the Stripe keys.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">PayUmoney settings:</span></h3></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Payment settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel,\" you can also change and update the PayUmoney account information. For this, you have to edit:&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Activation status</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Currency</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Test mode</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Test merchant key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Test merchant salt</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Live merchant key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Live merchant salt</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After providing the information, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update PayUmoney</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" settings for confirmation.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/ekattor-settings/updating-pay-u-money.png\" title=\"Updating Pay U Money\" alt=\"Updating Pay U Money\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Pay U Money\" alt=\"Updating Pay U Money\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 5.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating PayUmoney Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\