d: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 12.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Live Class&nbsp;</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To delete a live class, they have to select \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Delete</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Continue</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to confirm the action.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Student\'s panel:</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Your students have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the student panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Live class</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Your live class</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/introducing-your-live-class-student.png\" title=\"Introducing Your Live Class Student\" alt=\"Introducing Your Live Class Student\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Your Live Class Student\" alt=\"Introducing Your Live Class Student\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 13.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Live Class (Student)</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, they can overview:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Live class schedule</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Subject</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Meeting information (Your students can download the meeting information)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Join</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">They can join an online class by selecting the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Join</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/joining-class.png\" title=\"Joining Class\" alt=\"Joining Class\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Joining Class\" alt=\"Joining Class\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 14.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Joining a Live Class (Student)</span></span></h5>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(110, 158, '<div><font color=\"#0e101a\"><div><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">With this addon, you can enhance the feature of providing exam marks sending function to students and parents of your school. Configuring this addon, you can get the opportunity to send exam marks reports as an email to students and parents.</span></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To enhance this feature, you have to install this addon on your application. Now, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Before installing the process, we highly recommend you check your application version. For this, you have to navigate to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">About</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/check-update-ekattor-addon.png\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5 style=\"color: rgb(108, 117, 125);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Checking Application Version</span></span></h5><h5 style=\"color: rgb(108, 117, 125);\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">If you are running the mentioned version, then you are ready to install this addon.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Download the addon you want to install on your application from Codecanyon.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;Unzip the downloaded file.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You should get Two folders inside. One for documentation and the other for the addon file.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Do not try to remove or rename any folder.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go back to the application and log in as an admin.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Back office</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Addon manager</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add new addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li></ul><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/installing-a-addon-ekattor.png\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5 style=\"color: rgb(108, 117, 125);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Adding New Addon</span></span></h5><h5 style=\"color: rgb(108, 117, 125);\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the purchase code.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Upload the zip file from your device.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Install addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You will get a success message notification.</span></li></ul></div><div><br></div></font></div><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">In this school management system, only superadmin can use this addon. As a superadmin and admin, you have to navigate:</span><br></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the superadmin/admin panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Examination</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Send exam marks</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/introducing-send-exam-mark.png\" title=\"Introducing Send Exam Mark\" alt=\"Introducing Send Exam Mark\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Send Exam Mark\" alt=\"Introducing Send Exam Mark\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Send Exam Marks</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To send exam marks, you have to select:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Exam</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Section</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Receiver (You can send students or parents as a receiver)</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, you have to \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Show receiver</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button. Now you can overview the list of the receiver.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/show-receiver.png\" title=\"Show Receiver\" alt=\"Show Receiver\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Show Receiver\" alt=\"Show Receiver\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Showing Receivers</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To send the marks as an email, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Send mark</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option. Click the \"<b>Continue</b>\" button for confirmation.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/sending-mark.png\" title=\"Sending Mark\" alt=\"Sending Mark\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Sending Mark\" alt=\"Sending Mark\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 5.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Sending Marks&nbsp;</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also preview the email by selecting the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Preview</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/preview-marks-one.png\" title=\"Preview Marks One\" alt=\"Preview Marks One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Preview Marks One\" alt=\"Preview Marks One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/preview-marks-two.png\" title=\"Preview Marks Two\" alt=\"Preview Marks Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Preview Marks Two\" alt=\"Preview Marks Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 6.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Marks Preview</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After installing this addon, you have to configure the SMTP settings. For this, you have to click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Here</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/smtp-settings-mark-sender.png\" title=\"Smtp Settings Mark Sender\" alt=\"Smtp Settings Mark Sender\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Smtp Settings Mark Sender\" alt=\"Smtp Settings Mark Sender\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 7.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP SMTP Settings</span></span></h5>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(111, 159, '<p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Ekattor, you can manage previous information of students, events, alumni galleries with this addon. Configuring this addon, you can enhance the feature of all your past students. You can create, update, delete alumni information, events and gallery to your school.&nbsp;<br><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To enhance this feature, you have to install this addon on your application. Now, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Before installing the process, we highly recommend you check your application version. For this, you have to navigate to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">About</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/check-update-ekattor-addon.png\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Checking Application Version</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">If you are running the mentioned version, then you are ready to install this addon.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Download the addon you want to install on your application from Codecanyon.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;Unzip the downloaded file.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You should get Two folders inside. One for documentation and the other for the addon file.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Do not try to remove or rename any folder.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go back to the application and log in as an admin.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Back office</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Addon manager</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add new addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/installing-a-addon-ekattor.png\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Adding New Addons</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the purchase code.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Upload the zip file from your device.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Install addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You will get a success message notification.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Superadmin and admin can configure this panel. For this, you have to follow the steps:</span></p><ul><li style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the superadmin panel.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Alumni</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">To add a new alumni\'s information, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Alumni</strong><span xss=\"removed\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Manage alumni</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/introducing-manage-alumni.png\" title=\"Introducing Manage Alumni\" alt=\"Introducing Manage Alumni\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Manage Alumni\" alt=\"Introducing Manage Alumni\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Managing Alumni</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, you can overview:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Name of alumni</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Image&nbsp;</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Email</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Phone</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Profession</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Passing year</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To create a new alumni\'s directory, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Add new alumni</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/adding-new-alumni.png\" title=\"Adding New Alumni\" alt=\"Adding New Alumni\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Adding New Alumni\" alt=\"Adding New Alumni\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Adding New Alumni</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now you have to provide:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Alumni name</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Student code</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Email</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Phone number</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Passing section</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Profession</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Alumni image (You can upload the image from your device)</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After providing all information, click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Add alumni</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/creating-alumni-info.png\" title=\"Creating Alumni Info\" alt=\"Creating Alumni Info\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Creating Alumni Info\" alt=\"Creating Alumni Info\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 5.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Saving New Alumni</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To update the alumni\'s directory, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select alumni.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Edit</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Option</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, you have to change:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Alumni name</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Student code</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Email</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Phone number</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Passing section</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Profession</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Alumni image (You can upload the image from your device)</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After providing all information, click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update alumni</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your data.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/updating-alumni-info.png\" title=\"Updating Alumni Info\" alt=\"Updating Alumni Info\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Alumni Info\" alt=\"Updating Alumni Info\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 6.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Alumni</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To delete an alumni\'s directory, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Delete</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" Now, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Continue</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to confirm your action.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">In this panel, as a superadmin, you can create events for alumni. For this, you have to navigate:</span><br></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the superadmin panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Alumni</strong><span xss=\"removed\">\"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;</strong><span xss=\"removed\">option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Event</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/introducing-event-alumni.png\" title=\"Introducing Event Alumni\" alt=\"Introducing Event Alumni\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Event Alumni\" alt=\"Introducing Event Alumni\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 7.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Alumni Event&nbsp;</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, you can overview:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Frontend calendar</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event list</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event Photo</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event title</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event starting date</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event finishing date</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event visibility status</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section (You can edit and delete the event from here)</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">If you want to add a new event for alumni, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Add new event</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/adding-alumni-event.png\" title=\"Adding Alumni Event\" alt=\"Adding Alumni Event\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Adding Alumni Event\" alt=\"Adding Alumni Event\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 8.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Adding New Alumni Event</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this new form, you have to add:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event name</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event starting date</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event ending date</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Visibility option for frontend</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event photo (You can upload an image from your device)</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Save event</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your information.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/saving-new-alumni-event.png\" title=\"Saving New Alumni Event\" alt=\"Saving New Alumni Event\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Saving New Alumni Event\" alt=\"Saving New Alumni Event\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 9.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Saving New Alumni Event&nbsp;</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><em xss=\"removed\">Note:</em></strong><em xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;Your information will show on the frontend of your school website.</em></p><p xss=\"removed\"><em xss=\"removed\"><br></em></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To update the alumni event, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Edit</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" Now you have to provide:</span><br></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event name</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event starting date</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event ending date</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Visibility option for frontend</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Event photo (You can upload an image from your device)</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">event</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your information.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/updating-alumni-event.png\" title=\"Updating Alumni Event\" alt=\"Updating Alumni Event\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Alumni Event\" alt=\"Updating Alumni Event\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 10.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Alumni Event</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also remove the alumni event. All you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Delete</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" Then choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Continue</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button for confirmation.</span><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">To add a new gallery or photo for alumni, you have to follow the steps:</span><br></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the superadmin panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Alumni</strong><span xss=\"removed\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Gallery</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/introducing-gallery-alumni.png\" title=\"Introducing Gallery Alumni\" alt=\"Introducing Gallery Alumni\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Gallery Alumni\" alt=\"Introducing Gallery Alumni\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 11.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Alumni Gallery</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To add a new gallery for the alumni, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Add new gallery</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/creating-alumni-gallery.png\" title=\"Creating Alumni Gallery\" alt=\"Creating Alumni Gallery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Creating Alumni Gallery\" alt=\"Creating Alumni Gallery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 12.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Adding New Alumni Gallery</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this new form, you have to provide:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Gallery title</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Gallery description</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Visibility option for frontend</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Save gallery</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/adding-alumni-gallery.png\" title=\"Adding Alumni Gallery\" alt=\"Adding Alumni Gallery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Adding Alumni Gallery\" alt=\"Adding Alumni Gallery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 13.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Saving New Alumni Gallery</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update gallery</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option to save your changes.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, you can manage the gallery for different batches. For this, you have to select:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select an alumni gallery.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Edit</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Option</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Update the required information.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/updating-alumni-gallery.png\" title=\"Updating Alumni Gallery\" alt=\"Updating Alumni Gallery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Alumni Gallery\" alt=\"Updating Alumni Gallery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 14.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating Alumni Gallery</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also upload the image for an individual gallery. After uploading the image, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Save to gallery</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><em xss=\"removed\">Note:</em></strong><em xss=\"removed\">&nbsp;Your information will show on the frontend of your school website</em><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To remove the alumni\'s gallery, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Delete</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" Then select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Continue</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to complete your process.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also delete an image from the gallery. For this, you have to click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">More</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from the gallery.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/deleting-photo-alumni-gallery-one.png\" title=\"Deleting Photo Alumni Gallery One\" alt=\"Deleting Photo Alumni Gallery One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Deleting Photo Alumni Gallery One\" alt=\"Deleting Photo Alumni Gallery One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 15.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Deleting Alumni Photo-1</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Delete</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button. Then select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Continue</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button for confirmation.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/deleting-photo-alumni-gallery-two.png\" title=\"Deleting Photo Alumni Gallery Two\" alt=\"Deleting Photo Alumni Gallery Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Deleting Photo Alumni Gallery Two\" alt=\"Deleting Photo Alumni Gallery Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 16.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Deleting Alumni Photo-2</span></span></h5>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(112, 161, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Ekattor, you can use this addon to manage multiple branches of a school. After configuration, it will enhance the opportunity to create any number of school branches. You can switch to a single school anytime to manage the specific school data.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To install this addon on your application, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Before installing the process, we highly recommend you check your application version. For this, you have to navigate to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">About</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/check-update-ekattor-addon.png\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Checking Application Version</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">If you are running the mentioned version, then you are ready to install this addon.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Download the addon you want to install on your application from Codecanyon.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;Unzip the downloaded file.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You should get Two folders inside. One for documentation and the other for the addon file.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Do not try to remove or rename any folder.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go back to the application and log in as an admin.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Back office</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Addon manager</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add new addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/installing-a-addon-ekattor.png\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Adding New Addons</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the purchase code.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Upload the zip file from your device.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Install addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bot