(113, 160, '<p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">With this addon, you can take the attendance of students from the fingerprint reader service. After installing this addon will help you take the student attendance using the fingerprint reader machine and show the attendance report inside the application.<br><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To enhance this feature, you have to install this addon on your application. Now, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Before installing the process, we highly recommend you check your application version. For this, you have to navigate to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">About</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/check-update-ekattor-addon.png\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Checking Application Version</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">If you are running the mentioned version, then you are ready to install this addon.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Download the addon you want to install on your application from Codecanyon.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;Unzip the downloaded file.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You should get Two folders inside. One for documentation and the other for the addon file.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margi