strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/adding-biometric-attendance.png\" title=\"Adding Biometric Attendance\" alt=\"Adding Biometric Attendance\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Adding Biometric Attendance\" alt=\"Adding Biometric Attendance\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Taking Biometric Attendance</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, you have to select the addon file and upload it in this form. Then choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Upload file</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" to save your data.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/uploading-biometric-file.png\" title=\"Uploading Biometric File\" alt=\"Uploading Biometric File\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Uploading Biometric File\" alt=\"Uploading Biometric File\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Uploading File</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You have to configure the biometric attendance device with your application. Then register the student\'s information on this device.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/biometric-attendance-device.png\" title=\"Biometric Attendance Device\" alt=\"Biometric Attendance Device\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Biometric Attendance Device\" alt=\"Biometric Attendance Device\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 5.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Biometric Attendance Device</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After registering all information, a new form will appear on the screen. You have to select \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Import attendance</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" to take biometric attendance or select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Discard</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option for cancelation.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/importing-attendance.png\" title=\"Importing Attendance\" alt=\"Importing Attendance\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Importing Attendance\" alt=\"Importing Attendance\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 6.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Importing Attendance</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, you can overview the attendance report of the students. Here, you can also \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Filter</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" the report card by selecting:</span><br></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Month</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Session</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Section</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/biometric-attendance-report-card.png\" title=\"Biometric Attendance Report Card\" alt=\"Biometric Attendance Report Card\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Biometric Attendance Report Card\" alt=\"Biometric Attendance Report Card\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 7.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Attendance Report Card</span></span></h5>', 1),
(114, 163, '<p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">With this addon, you can create and print a student\'s Id card. Installing this addon on your application will allow you to print any student’s ID card for your school.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To enhance this feature, you have to install this addon on your application. Now, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Before installing the process, we highly recommend you check your application version. For this, you have to navigate to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">About</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/check-update-ekattor-addon.png\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Checking Application Version</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">If you are running the mentioned version, then you are ready to install this addon.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Download the addon you want to install on your application from Codecanyon.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;Unzip the downloaded file.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You should get Two folders inside. One for documentation and the other for the addon file.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Do not try to remove or rename any folder.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go back to the application and log in as an admin.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Back office</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Addon manager</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add new addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/installing-a-addon-ekattor.png\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Adding New Addons</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the purchase code.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Upload the zip file from your device.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Install addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You will get a success message notification.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">To create an ID card, you have to follow the steps:</span><br></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the user panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Student</strong><span xss=\"removed\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select a student\'s \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Option</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Generate id card</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/introducing-id-card.png\" title=\"Introducing Id Card\" alt=\"Introducing Id Card\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Id Card\" alt=\"Introducing Id Card\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Generating ID Card</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After previewing the ID card, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Print</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/print-id-card.png\" title=\"Print Id Card\" alt=\"Print Id Card\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Print Id Card\" alt=\"Print Id Card\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Printing ID Card&nbsp;</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">That\'s it!</span></p>', 1);
