(115, 162, '<p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">With this addon, you can enhance the feature of sending SMS to other users of your school. This addon will help you to send important notices, messages to the students, teachers, and parents.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To enhance this feature, you have to install this addon on your application. Now, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Before installing the process, we highly recommend you check your application version. For this, you have to navigate to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">About</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/check-update-ekattor-addon.png\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" alt=\"Check Update Ekattor Addon\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Checking Application Version</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">If you are running the mentioned version, then you are ready to install this addon.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Download the addon you want to install on your application from Codecanyon.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;Unzip the downloaded file.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You should get Two folders inside. One for documentation and the other for the addon file.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Do not try to remove or rename any folder.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go back to the application and log in as an admin.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Back office</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Addon manager</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add new addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/installing-a-addon-ekattor.png\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" alt=\"Installing A Addon Ekattor\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Adding New Addons</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the purchase code.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Upload the zip file from your device.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Install addon</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You will get a success message notification.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">After installing the application, you have to follow the steps below:</span><br></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the user panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Back office</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">SMS center</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/introducing-sms-center.png\" title=\"Introducing Sms Center\" alt=\"Introducing Sms Center\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Sms Center\" alt=\"Introducing Sms Center\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP SMS Center&nbsp;</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After opening the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">SMS center</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel, you have to configure the SMS settings. For this, you have to navigate:</span></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the user panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Back office</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">SMS center</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">SMS settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\">.</span><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\"&nbsp;</span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After opening this panel, you have to select and activate the SMS gateway.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/activiting-sms-gateway.png\" title=\"Activiting Sms Gateway\" alt=\"Activiting Sms Gateway\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Activiting Sms Gateway\" alt=\"Activiting Sms Gateway\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Activating SMS Gateway</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Next, you have to configure the Twilio settings. For this, you have to provide:</span><br></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Twilio SID</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Twilio token</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Twilio sender phone number</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After providing data, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update SMS settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your settings.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/twilio-settings.png\" title=\"Twilio Settings\" alt=\"Twilio Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Twilio Settings\" alt=\"Twilio Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 5.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating SMS Settings-1</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To configure the MSG91 settings panel, you have to provide:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">MSG91 authentication key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">MSG91 sender ID</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">MSG91 route</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">MSG91 country code</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update SMS settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button for confirmation.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/msg91-settings.png\" title=\"Msg91 Settings\" alt=\"Msg91 Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Msg91 Settings\" alt=\"Msg91 Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 6.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Updating SMS Settings-2</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After configuring the SMS settings, you can send SMS to the teachers, parents, and students. For this, you have to follow the steps:</span></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the user panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Back office</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">SMS center</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Send SMS</strong><span xss=\"removed\">.</span><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\"&nbsp;</span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To send SMS, you have to select the receivers. You have to choose:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Receiver (Teachers/Students/Parents)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Section</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After choosing the receivers, click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Show receivers</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now you can overview the receivers list. Here, you can select the specific receiver or all receivers. For this, you have to click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Check all</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/selecting-receivers.png\" title=\"Selecting Receivers\" alt=\"Selecting Receivers\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Selecting Receivers\" alt=\"Selecting Receivers\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 7.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Selecting SMS Receivers</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After writing the message or notice, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Send SMS</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/send-SMS.png\" title=\"Send SMS\" alt=\"Send SMS\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Send SMS\" alt=\"Send SMS\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 8.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP Sending SMS</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can overview and change the SMS settings by clicking the \"<b>Here</b>\" option on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Instruction</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/addons/sms-instruction-panel.png\" title=\"Sms Instruction Panel\" alt=\"Sms Instruction Panel\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Sms Instruction Panel\" alt=\"Sms Instruction Panel\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\" xss=\"removed\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 9.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ekattor ERP SMS Instruction Option</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">That\'s it!</span></p>', 1),
(116, 197, '<p>Configuring the Ekattor school management system is the first step to take after purchase. The installation of this application process is simple. In this doc, we will see the way of installing Ekattor ERP.<br><br></p><p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/JDgTWs-coZ4\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"note-video-clip\"></iframe><br></p>', 1),
(117, 198, '<p>In this school management system, you can admit students in 3 ways. They are-</p><ul><li>Single student admission</li><li>Bulk student admission</li><li>Excel upload</li></ul><p>We will show you how you can admit students to Ekattor in this documentation.</p><p><br>&lt;iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/c8JkgToLM70\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"note-video-clip\"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;<br></p>', 1),
(118, 199, '<p>As a superadmin, admin, and teacher can take student\'s attendance to track academic progress in Ekattor. In this doc, we will help you with how to take attendance in Ekattor.<br><br></p><p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/fQPYzax_yeU\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"note-video-clip\"></iframe><br></p>', 1),
(119, 200, '<p>This doc will show you how to manage your school\'s class routine and syllabus in this application.<br><br></p><p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/MvdGb2mACWM\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"note-video-clip\"></iframe><br></p>', 1),
(120, 201, '<p>Class and subject are the crucial parts of the school academic sector. Here, you can see how to manage the class and subject in this school management system.<br><br></p><p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/Xkma3H9iz84\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"note-video-clip\"></iframe><br></p>', 1),
(121, 202, '<p>In Ekattor, you can create, modify and remove the class, section, subject from the academic panel. Here, we will show you how to manage class and subject in your application.<br><br></p><p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/Xkma3H9iz84\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"note-video-clip\"></iframe><br></p>', 1),
(122, 203, '<p>The academic calendar is an essential part of the academic panel, and it helps to make track of an academic session. In this doc, you can see how to manage the event calendar in Ekattor.<br><br></p><p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/NmEUkswtRMM\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"note-video-clip\"></iframe><br></p>', 1),
(123, 204, '<p>The examination is a great way to evaluate what the students have learned concerning particular subjects, and it shows the path of learning. Exam and marks are part of the examination panel. In this documentation, we will show you how to manage class and subject in your application.<br></p><p><br></p><p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/OkDiZvNPicQ\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"note-video-clip\"></iframe><br></p>', 1),
(124, 167, '<p></p><p>In Mastery, a class is a set of lessons, and the admin and instructor can create different lessons under one class.&nbsp;<span xss=\"removed\">Students can watch the paid or free lessons in one class. Admin and instructor can add several lessons under one class and subject.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p>\r\n<p></p>', 1),
(125, 168, '<p>The role of an instructor is oriented to teaching. An instructor can create the course and send the lesson approval request to the admin. </p><p><span xss=removed>Instructors can provide Youtube, Vimeo video, Html5 video URL, and you can also upload the video file from your device. An instructor can also manage the classes, review classes, remove the classes, answer students\' questions, and many more. Instructors teach courses in their area of expertise and develop an instructional plan and assignments for students.</span><br></p>', 1),
(126, 169, '<p>A student is a learner or someone who attends an educational institution. The role of students has the highest number of users in the Mastery LMS platform. </p><p><span xss=removed>A student is primarily a person who is enrolled in a school or other educational institution and learning knowledge, developing professions, and achieving employment in the desired field.</span><br></p>', 1),
(127, 170, '<p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Only the Admin has the highest number of privileges and permissions in Mastery LMS. The admin is responsible for managing a computer or network, and the admin has full access to the hardware and software.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">An admin can:</span><br></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Configure and manage the application.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage users</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Add new classes.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Approve teacher\'s lesson request.&nbsp;</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Create new categories.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Add new skills.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Overview transaction history.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage the subscription package.</span></li></ul>', 1),
(128, 171, '<p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\">System Settings:</strong></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">First of all, to operate the Mastery LMS, you have to configure the settings from the admin panel to update the Youtube and Vimeo API keys. For this, you have to navigate:</span></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the admin panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">System setting</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/introducing-system-setting.png\" title=\"Introducing System Setting\" alt=\"Introducing System Setting\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing System Setting\" alt=\"Introducing System Setting\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS System Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this settings panel, you have to provide:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Youtube API key</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Vimeo API key</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, to create and upload a lesson on Mastery LMS, select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Save changes</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option for confirmation.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/youtube-vimeo-api-key.png\" title=\"Youtube Vimeo Api Key\" alt=\"Youtube Vimeo Api Key\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Youtube Vimeo Api Key\" alt=\"Youtube Vimeo Api Key\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Saving System Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><h3><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"\">Payment settings:</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After configuring the system settings, you have to manage the payment settings. For this, you have to follow the steps below:</span></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the admin panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Settings</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Payment setting</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.<br><br></span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/introducing-payment-settings.png\" title=\"Introducing Payment Settings\" alt=\"Introducing Payment Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Payment Settings\" alt=\"Introducing Payment Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Payment Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, you have to configure the currency settings. For this, you have to provide:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">System currency(You can set any currency)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Position of the currency</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now to save data, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update system currency</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.&nbsp;</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/updating-system-currency.png\" title=\"Updating System Currency\" alt=\"Updating System Currency\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating System Currency\" alt=\"Updating System Currency\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Updating System Currency&nbsp;</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br>After configuring the currency settings, you have set the transaction media settings. We support:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Paypal</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Stripe</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"\">PayPal:</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To active the payment gateways, you have to configure the Paypal settings. For this, you have to provide:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Activation status</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Mode</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Paypal currency</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Sandbox client ID</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Sandbox secret key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Production client ID</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Production secret key</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After that, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update PayPal keys</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your information.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/updating-paypal-keys.png\" title=\"Updating Paypal Keys\" alt=\"Updating Paypal Keys\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Paypal Keys\" alt=\"Updating Paypal Keys\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 5.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Updating PayPal keys</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To get the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Client ID</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" and \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Secret key</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" for your PayPal account, you have to follow the steps below:</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Navigate to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">PayPal Developers Website</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" home page.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the dashboard.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also log in with your mobile number using OTP.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set up the profile.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Your Name</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Dashboard</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" in the top right corner.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Create App</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" to create a new app.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the details for the new app.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now you can see the PayPal Client Id and secret.</span></li></ul><h3><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"\"><br></span></h3><h3><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"\">Stripe:</span></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After configuring the Paypal settings, you have to set the Stripe settings. For this, you have to select:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Activation status</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Test mode</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Stripe currency</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Test secret key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Test public key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Live secret key</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">live public key</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, you have to click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update Stripe keys</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button for confirmation.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/updating-stripe-keys.png\" title=\"Updating Stripe Keys\" alt=\"Updating Stripe Keys\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Stripe Keys\" alt=\"Updating Stripe Keys\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 6.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Updating Stripe Keys</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></p></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To get the Stripe API Keys, please follow the steps below:</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to your Stripe dashboard.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Navigate to the&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">API&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Toggle the option that says \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Viewing test data</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Viewing live data</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Reveal live key token</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now you can see the Stripe keys.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">That\'s it!</span></p>', 1),
(129, 4, '<p><strong xss=\"removed\">Lorem Ipsum</strong><span xss=\"removed\"> is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/ekattor-erp/managing-user-ekattor/introducing-students.png\" title=\"Introducing Students\" alt=\"Introducing Students\" xss=removed><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></p>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(130, 175, '<p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Mastery, an admin and instructor can create a lesson or a class for the students. Also, they can create many lessons under one subject and one class.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><strong xss=\"removed\"><br></strong></p><h3><strong xss=\"removed\">Admin panel:</strong></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">As an admin, to create a class, you have to navigate:</span></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the admin panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Class</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li></ol><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, you can:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage class</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lesson</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Activation status&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">View class in the frontend frontend</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Mark class as pending review</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Approve teacher\'s request</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To manage the published class, you have to follow the following steps below:</span></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the admin panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Class</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">All classes</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.<br><br></span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/introducing-all-classes-panel-mastery.png\" title=\"Introducing All Classes Panel Mastery\" alt=\"Introducing All Classes Panel Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing All Classes Panel Mastery\" alt=\"Introducing All Classes Panel Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS All Classes</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Here, you can overview:&nbsp;</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class title</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Category</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lesson</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Status</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Action</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel for more option</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Action</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel, you can:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">View class in frontend</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Update class</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Change activation status</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Mark a class for pending review</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Delete the class</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/class-option.png\" title=\"Class Option\" alt=\"Class Option\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Class Option\" alt=\"Class Option\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Class Options</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To overview your class in the frontend, you have to click the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">View in frontend</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Action</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\"</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/class-frontend.png\" title=\"Class Frontend\" alt=\"Class Frontend\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Class Frontend\" alt=\"Class Frontend\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Class Frontend</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Here, you can preview:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class&nbsp;</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lesson&nbsp;</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class summary</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class discussion</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Save</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" and \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Share</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To update the class, you have to  navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Manage class</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Acton</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Open the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Class information</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, you have to update:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class title.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Category.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">level.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Skills. (You can add more than one skill)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Highlight the class. (You can consider your as free/subscription-based, mark as featured, recommended on the website, or add the class as a home page slider)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class thumbnail. (You can select from your device)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class banner. (You can select from your device)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Short description.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Long description.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"></p><p></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After providing the information, you have to select the \"</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Save change</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your data.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/managing-class-one-mastery.png\" title=\"Managing Class One Mastery\" alt=\"Managing Class One Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Managing Class One Mastery\" alt=\"Managing Class One Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/managing-class-two-mastery.png\" title=\"Managing Class Two Mastery\" alt=\"Managing Class Two Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Managing Class Two Mastery\" alt=\"Managing Class Two Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Managing Class</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Note:</em></strong><em style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">&nbsp;If you add the class for free in the \"<b>highlight the class</b>\" option, all the lessons will be considered free.</em><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To change the activation status of a class, you have to follow the steps below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Mark as active/inactive</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">All class</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Yes</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button for confirmation.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">As an admin, you can select a class pending review. For this, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Mark as pending for review</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">All class</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Yes</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button for confirmation.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To delete a class, you have to select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Delete</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Action</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" Then select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Yes</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save your information.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To add a new class in the Mastery, you have to follow the steps:</span></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the admin panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Class</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Add new classes</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/introducing-add-new-class-mastery.png\" title=\"Introducing Add New Class Mastery\" alt=\"Introducing Add New Class Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Add New Class Mastery\" alt=\"Introducing Add New Class Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"r