"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Mark as active/inactive</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">All class</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"<b>Yes</b>\" button for confirmation.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To delete their class, they have to select the \"</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">Delete</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">Action</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" Now, select the \"</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">Yes</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to confirm the action.</span><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;\">To add a new class in the Mastery, your teachers have to follow the steps:</span><br></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the teacher panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Class</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Add new classes</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" panel.</span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/introducing-add-new-class-teacher-mastery.png\" title=\"Introducing Add New Class Teacher Mastery\" alt=\"Introducing Add New Class Teacher Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Add New Class Teacher Mastery\" alt=\"Introducing Add New Class Teacher Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 11.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Adding New Class (Instructor)</span></span></h5><h5><br></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, your teachers can create a new class for the student. For this, they have to provide:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class title</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Category</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">level</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Skills (They can add more than one skill)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Highlight the class (They can consider your as free/subscription-based, mark as featured, recommended on the website, or add the class as a home page slider)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class thumbnail (They can select from your device)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Class banner (They can select from your device)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Short description</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Long description</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After providing the information, your teachers have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Save and next</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to save their data.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/creating-new-class-teacher-mastery-one.png\" title=\"Creating New Class Teacher Mastery One\" alt=\"Creating New Class Teacher Mastery One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Creating New Class Teacher Mastery One\" alt=\"Creating New Class Teacher Mastery One\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/creating-new-class-teacher-mastery-two.png\" title=\"Creating New Class Teacher Mastery Two\" alt=\"Creating New Class Teacher Mastery Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Creating New Class Teacher Mastery Two\" alt=\"Creating New Class Teacher Mastery Two\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 12.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Saving New Class (Instructor)</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"></p><p></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><em style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Note:</span></em></strong><em style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;After creating the class, their new class will be pending for admin\'s review. If the admin approves your request, the teacher\'s class will be ready for students.</span></em></p>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(131, 176, '<p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">As we all know, the admin and teacher can create the class and lesson in Mastery LMS.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><font color=\"#000000\"><b><br></b></font></p><h3><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"\">Admin panel:</font></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">As an admin, to manage the lesson, you have to navigate:</span></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the admin panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Class</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">All classes</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Action</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" section.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Manage class</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Lesson</strong><span xss=\"removed\">.</span><span xss=\"removed\">\"</span></li></ol><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, you can:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Add</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Edit</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Remove</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">View the front-end</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Sort lessons</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To add a new lesson, you have to select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add new lesson</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/adding-new-lesson-mastery.png\" title=\"Adding New Lesson Mastery\" alt=\"Adding New Lesson Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Adding New Lesson Mastery\" alt=\"Adding New Lesson Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Adding New Lesson</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\">Here, you have to provide:</p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lesson title</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lesson type (You can select Youtube, Vimeo, HTML5, or you can upload video from your device)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Blank box</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" if you want to keep your lesson for everyone.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Upload lesson</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to create a new lesson.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/creating-a-new-lesson-mastery.png\" title=\"Creating A New Lesson Mastery\" alt=\"Creating A New Lesson Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Creating A New Lesson Mastery\" alt=\"Creating A New Lesson Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Uploading Lesson</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Preview</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Modify</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Delete</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Sort lessons&nbsp;</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/lesson-option-mastery.png\" title=\"Lesson Option Mastery\" alt=\"Lesson Option Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Lesson Option Mastery\" alt=\"Lesson Option Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Lesson Option Mastery\" alt=\"Lesson Option Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Lesson Option</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can preview your lesson by selecting the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">View on frontend</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option. Here, you can share, save and discuss the lesson with students.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\">To update or modify the lesson, you have to select the \"<b>Edit</b>\" button. You can change:</p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lesson title</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lesson type (You can select Youtube, Vimeo, HTML5, or you can upload video from your device)</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Blank box</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" if you want to keep your lesson for everyone.</span></li></ul><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Update lesson</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to create a new lesson.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/updating-lesson-admin-mastery.png].png\" title=\"Updating Lesson Admin Mastery.png]\" alt=\"Updating Lesson Admin Mastery.png]\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Lesson Admin Mastery.png]\" alt=\"Updating Lesson Admin Mastery.png]\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Updating Lesson</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To delete your lesson, you have to select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Delete</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button from \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Action</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" and select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Yes</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to confirm your action.</span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p><p xss=\"removed\"><font color=\"#000000\">You can also sort the lesson in the class.</font><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><h3><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"\">Teacher panel:</font></h3><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To manage the lesson, your teachers have to navigate:</span></p><ol xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the teacher panel.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Class</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from the left menu.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">All classes</strong><span xss=\"removed\">.\"</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Action</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Manage class</strong><span xss=\"removed\">.</span><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\"</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong xss=\"removed\">Lesson</strong><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li></ol><p xss=\"removed\"><br></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/introducing-teacher-lesson-panel.png\" title=\"Introducing Teacher Lesson Panel\" alt=\"Introducing Teacher Lesson Panel\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Teacher Lesson Panel\" alt=\"Introducing Teacher Lesson Panel\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 5.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS All Classes (Teacher)</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Here, they can:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Add</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Edit</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Remove</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">View the front-end</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Sort the lesson</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To add a new lesson, your teachers have to select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add new lesson</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/adding-new-lesson-teacher-mastery.png\" title=\"Adding New Lesson Teacher Mastery\" alt=\"Adding New Lesson Teacher Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Adding New Lesson Teacher Mastery\" alt=\"Adding New Lesson Teacher Mastery\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 6.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mastery LMS Adding New Lesson (Teacher)</span></span></h5><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this panel, your teachers have to provide:</span></p><ul xss=\"removed\"><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lesson title.</span></li><li xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\" data-prese