(138, 184, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Mastery LMS is a subscription-based learning platform. Students have to purchase a subscription to watch all videos. As an admin, you can manage the subscription package.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 0.875rem;\">For this, you have to navigate:</span><br></p><ol style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the admin panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Packages</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li></ol><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/mastery-lms/setting-up-the-class/introducing-package.png\" title=\"Introducing Package\" alt=\"Introducing Package\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Package\" alt=\"Introducing Package\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Introducing Package\" alt=\"Introducing Pack