(179, 77, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">An instructor can create and sell the course based on their expertise field. In Academy LMS, an instructor have to share the course revenue with the admin. As an admin, you can manage the percentage of commissions from the panel. For this, you have to follow the steps below:</span></p><ol style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the admin panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">User</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Instructor</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserv