in-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/academy-lms/administrative-controls/currency-settings-academy.png\" title=\"Currency Settings Academy\" alt=\"Currency Settings Academy\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Currency Settings Academy\" alt=\"Currency Settings Academy\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span xss=\"removed\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span></strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Academy LMS Updating System Currency</span></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Note:</em></strong><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;Make sure that your \"</em><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">System currency</em></strong><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" and other gateway currency are the same.</em></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">PayPal gateway:</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top