(283, 343, '<h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Getting started:</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can overview their assigned orders through the mobile application using the best flexibility. To get the delivery boy mobile application, they can follow the steps below:</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Download:</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can download the mobile application from the Google Playstore/App Store or get the application download link from their admin site. It will depend on how the site admin distributes the application file.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Installation:</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After downloading the APK file, the delivery boy has to install the application on their mobile device. Then they have to provide 