(288, 353, '<p>Checkout online grocery store is created based on managing order systems. The order will be generated when a customer purchases products from your online grocery store. Here, you have to update products, manage orders from the customers and deliver products through the delivery boy app. Customers can make payments for their orders through three different gateway systems and cash on delivery service. If the payment is in cash on delivery, the delivery boy will receive the payment after delivery.&nbsp;<br></p>', 1),
