(290, 355, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Getting started:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can overview their assigned orders through the mobile application using the best flexibility. To get the delivery boy mobile application, they can follow the steps below:</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Download:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can download the mobile application from the Google Playstore/App Store or get the application download link from their admin site. It will depend on how the site admin distributes the application file.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Installation:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After downloading the APK file, the delivery boy has to install the application on their mobile device. Then they have to provide application permission to continue the installation process. After completing the installation process, they can use the Checkout delivery boy mobile application.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Pending orders:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After opening the application, the delivery boy can overview their assigned pending orders. They complete their delivery by following this pending orders list.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">[checkout-completed-order.png]</span></p>', 1),
(291, 356, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Getting started:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can overview their assigned orders through the mobile application using the best flexibility. To get the delivery boy mobile application, they can follow the steps below:</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Download:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can download the mobile application from the Google Playstore/App Store or get the application download link from their admin site. It will depend on how the site admin distributes the application file.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Installation:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After downloading the APK file, the delivery boy has to install the application on their mobile device. Then they have to provide application permission to continue the installation process. After completing the installation process, they can use the Checkout delivery boy mobile application.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Pending orders:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After opening the application, the delivery boy can overview their assigned pending orders. They complete their delivery by following this pending orders list.</span></p><p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"></p></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">[checkout-completed-order.png]</span></p>', 1),
(292, 357, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Getting started:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can overview their assigned orders through the mobile application using the best flexibility. To get the delivery boy mobile application, they can follow the steps below:</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Download:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can download the mobile application from the Google Playstore/App Store or get the application download link from their admin site. It will depend on how the site admin distributes the application file.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Installation:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After downloading the APK file, the delivery boy has to install the application on their mobile device. Then they have to provide application permission to continue the installation process. After completing the installation process, they can use the Checkout delivery boy mobile application.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Pending orders:</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After opening the application, the delivery boy can overview their assigned pending orders. They complete their delivery by following this pending orders list.</span></p><p></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"></p><p></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/checkout/checkout-delivery-boy-mobile-app/checkout-completed-order.png\" title=\"Checkout Completed Order\" alt=\"Checkout Completed Order\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Checkout Completed Order\" alt=\"Checkout Completed Order\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout&nbsp;Mobile Application Completed Orders (Delivery Boy)</span></span></h5>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(293, 358, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can update the order status by completing the delivery. To update the order status, they have to follow the steps:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Your delivery boy can select a product from the pending order list.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Your delivery boy can complete the delivery by getting help from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Call</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" and \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Direction</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" buttons. Your delivery boy can converse with customers through the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Call</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button and get the delivery location from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Direction</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/checkout/checkout-delivery-boy-mobile-app/call-and-direction-button-checkout.png\" title=\"Call And Direction Button Checkout\" alt=\"Call And Direction Button Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Call And Direction Button Checkout\" alt=\"Call And Direction Button Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout&nbsp;Mobile Application Call &amp; Direction (Delivery Boy)</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After delivering the product, the delivery boy can update the status from their mobile application. If the delivery boy delivered the products, they have to tick on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Product Delivered</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option. If the delivery is in cash on delivery (COD), the delivery boy has to receive the payment and tick on the second option. After that, they have to click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update Order</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button to update the delivery status.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/checkout/checkout-delivery-boy-mobile-app/delivery-status-update-checkout.png\" title=\"Delivery Status Update Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Status Update Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Delivery Status Update Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Status Update Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout&nbsp;Mobile Application Updating Order Info (Delivery Boy)</span></span></h5>', 1),
(294, 359, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Your delivery boy can overview their completed orders from this mobile application. They can also search orders with customized date filtering features.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/checkout/checkout-delivery-boy-mobile-app/delivery-completed-order-checkout.png\" title=\"Delivery Completed Order Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Completed Order Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Delivery Completed Order Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Completed Order Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout&nbsp;Mobile Application Completed Orders (Delivery Boy)</span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;After clicking an order, your delivery boy can overview:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Product summary</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Product quantity</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Subtotal amount</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Tax</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Delivery charge</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Total amount</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Customer details</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/checkout/checkout-delivery-boy-mobile-app/delivered-order-details-checkout.png\" title=\"Delivered Order Details Checkout\" alt=\"Delivered Order Details Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Delivered Order Details Checkout\" alt=\"Delivered Order Details Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout&nbsp;Mobile Application Order Details (Delivery Boy)</span></span></h5>', 1),
(295, 360, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this mobile application, the delivery boy can update their profile info. But only the site admin can create an account for the delivery boy. The delivery boy can log in from their mobile device. To manage the account info, the delivery boy has to follow the steps below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Profile</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Edit</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/checkout/checkout-delivery-boy-mobile-app/delivery-boy-account-edit-button-checkout.png\" title=\"Delivery Boy Account Edit Button Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Boy Account Edit Button Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Delivery Boy Account Edit Button Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Boy Account Edit Button Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout&nbsp;Mobile Application Editing Account Info (Delivery Boy)</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Update required information.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can also change their password from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Profile</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option. After that, select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Change Password</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" menu. To update the password, they have to provide:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Current password.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">New password.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Again new password for confirmation.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/checkout/checkout-delivery-boy-mobile-app/delivery-boy-password-update-button-checkout.png\" title=\"Delivery Boy Password Update Button Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Boy Password Update Button Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Delivery Boy Password Update Button Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Boy Password Update Button Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout&nbsp;Mobile Application Updating Password (Delivery Boy)</span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The delivery boy can also sign out from their account from the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Sign Out</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></p>', 1),
(296, 361, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can overview the payment history of your grocery store at a glance in Checkout with a customized filtering option. Here, you can see:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Order ID</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Total amount (Individual order)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Payment method</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Order status</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Order date</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Action</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button for print invoice</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To overview your payment history, you have to follow the steps below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the admin panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Payment history</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from the left menu.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/checkout/order-management/payment-history-checkout.png\" title=\"Payment History Checkout\" alt=\"Payment History Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Payment History Checkout\" alt=\"Payment History Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout&nbsp;Payment History</span></span></h5>', 1),
(297, 362, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Checkout, an admin can only create the delivery boy account. The site admin will provide a password and an Email ID to the delivery boy to complete the delivery.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To log in to the mobile application, the delivery boy has to follow the steps below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Open the application after installation.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide Email ID&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide password</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Sign in</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/checkout/checkout-delivery-boy-mobile-app/delivery-boy-sign-in-checkout.png\" title=\"Delivery Boy Sign In Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Boy Sign In Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Delivery Boy Sign In Checkout\" alt=\"Delivery Boy Sign In Checkout\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Checkout&nbsp;Mobile Application Sign In (Delivery Boy)</span></span></h5>', 1),
(298, 363, '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">What is Learny LMS</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Learny learning management system (LMS) is a WordPress plugin. It is an educational platform where instructors and students achieve or share their knowledge or skills in a course-based system, and the admin has to manage the plugin system.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">What is a WordPress plugin?</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">WordPress is a PHP language-based content management system (CMS). It\'s a free and open-source platform and the most powerful website builder in the website creation community.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">A plugin is a part of the software that contains functions and adds to the WordPress website. It helps enhance workability and add more features to your WordPress website. These pieces of software are also written in the PHP language.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">What Learny does</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Learny is the best course-based learning management system for you. With this plugin, you can:&nbsp;</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Create course</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Add section</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage lessons and notes</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Add instructor</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage students</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Explore by browsing the course portal</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Course enrollment</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Create wishlist</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">View course progress</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Revenue reports</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Share revenue</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage settings</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Who is Learny LMS for</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Learny LMS is an educational platform. Basically, this robust learning management system is programmed for students, instructors, and the site admin (author).</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">An admin is the most responsible and privileged user in Learny LMS. An admin has to manage the other users in this platform, configure the settings, manage the course category, etc. Also, an admin can create the course and make money.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">An instructor can create a course to share their knowledge and earn by selling the course. They can use multiple platforms in this learning management system to create the course, lessons, notes, etc. An instructor can earn commission by selling their courses.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Students can enrich their knowledge, update their skills by enrolling in a suitable course on this platform. This WordPress plugin is also beneficial for the new employee for training purposes.</span></p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-size: 1.14844rem; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: transparent;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: transparent;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: transparent;\"><br style=\"font-family: Nunito, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400;\"></p></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"></p>', 1),
(299, 364, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can quickly start your learning management and earn money by selling the course with Learny. Follow the quick start guide to sell your course below:</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">1. Purchase</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Learny learning management system is a robust WordPress plugin. You can purchase the Learny LMS Pro version from the official website of Codecanyon.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">2. Installation&nbsp;</span></h3><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\"><br></font></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\">The installation process of Learny LMS is as easy and simple as other WordPress plugins. After purchasing the plugin from codecanyon, log in to your WordPress website as Admin. Then go to the \"Add new plugin\" menu option and upload the plugin zip file. Hit the \"Install Now\" button and after then activate the plugin.</font><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">3. Configuration</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After completing the installation and activation, as an Admin you have to configure the necessary settings to run the business. To quickly start your website, you have to configure:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Page Settings</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">General Settings</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">API Settings</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Payment Settings</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;You can find these settings options from <b>Learny LMS</b> &gt; <b>Plugin Settings.</b></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/what-is-learny-lms/configuration-learny.png\" title=\"Configuration Learny\" alt=\"Configuration Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Configuration Learny\" alt=\"Configuration Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Course creation</span></h3><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\"><br></font></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\">To add courses, go to <b>Courses</b> &gt; <b>Add new courses</b>.&nbsp; Here you can provide all the necessary details about the course and hit the \"<b>Publish</b>\" button to publish a course.</font><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Purchasing the course</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Students can purchase any published courses. They can simply browse the website to find the best course for them. They can also search and filter for their desired course. After that, they can purchase the course through a payment gateway.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/what-is-learny-lms/purchasing-course-learny.png\" title=\"Purchasing Course Learny\" alt=\"Purchasing Course Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Purchasing Course Learny\" alt=\"Purchasing Course Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Gateway</span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\">Learning</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After purchasing, students can start learning the course. While learning the course, they can monitor their improvement through the course progress bar. Also, they can add favorite courses to the wishlist, overview purchase history.</span></p>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(300, 365, '<h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Course</span></h3><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\"><br></font></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\">Learny LMS is a course-based online platform. The course acts as a medium for gathering students and instructors to share and enrich knowledge or skills in this learning platform.</font></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\">An educator creates the course for the students in their expertise. An instructor can add several lessons, quizzes, and notes to a course. They can also earn by selling the course. On the other side, students can enrich their knowledge or upgrade their skills by watching the courses and completing the notes.</font></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lesson</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">A lesson is a small unit of a course. You can create lessons on a specific topic under a course. There are multiple lessons in a course. Create and add lessons on multiple topics to make the course more effective and resourceful.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Section</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">A section is a part of the course curriculum. There can be multiple sections to a course. You can add several lessons to a section. Also, you can sort your section by dragging and dropping.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Curriculum</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">A curriculum consists of the \"<b>Roadmap</b>\" of any course. In Learny LMS, the curriculum will help you overview the course details. For example:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Section</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Course lessons or note</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Course lesson duration</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">A course curriculum will help your students get external info and a course summary.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Tag</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Leanry LMS, you can add multiple keywords for a course. These all keywords are individual tags. Showing related courses based on tags and even course searching can be happened with it.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Admin</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Learny LMS, an admin has to perform a large number of activities. The admin has the most privilege and responsibility in this platform, and an admin is responsible for every curriculum activity.&nbsp;An admin can:</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p><p></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;; list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Configuring necessary settings.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;; list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage all user profiles.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;; list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage courses.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;; list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage course category.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;; list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage instructor payout requests.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;; list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Manage payment reports etc.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Instructor</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\">The center of every educational platform is \"<b>Learning</b>.\" In Learny LMS, an instructor can create and sell the course.</font></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\"><br></font></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><font color=\"#0e101a\">An instructor can add lessons, notes to make the course more resourceful. They can also update, modify, and the course if they want. An instructor can earn by selling the course from this platform. For this, they have to share a percentage with the admin. After all, an instructor can build a career in Learny LMS.</font></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Student</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Learny LMS, a student is a user who enrolls in different subjects/courses to enrich knowledge or upgrade their skills.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Here, a student can enroll in a course by purchasing it. After purchasing the course, they can:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Browse all the available courses.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Add them to their wishlist.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Purchase course.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Start learning the course.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Get the notes and attachments.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Track their purchase history.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">This learning management system provides the best user experience with user-friendly features to every user.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Category</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can classify courses so that your students can find the course more quickly. You can add several categories and sub-categories according to the courses.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">WooCommerce</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">WooCommerce is the most popular e-commerce plugin for WordPress. Learny LMS is compatible with it. You can sell all the premium courses through WooCommerce with just one click.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Elementor</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Elementor is one of the most popular page builder plugins for your WordPress website. It is an all-in-one solution for you. Just drag and drop the widgets and build a page. With this plugin, you can customize every part of your website.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Learny Elementor Widget</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Learny comes with several necessary Elementor widgets that every LMS system should have. You can create an LMS page from the ground without any coding experience. Just drag-drop available Learny Elementor Widgets, that\'s all you need to do!</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p>', 1),
(301, 366, '<h2 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;; font-weight: normal;\"></h2><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Learny LMS is an educational platform where instructors and students achieve or share their knowledge or skills in a course-based system, and the admin has to manage the plugin system.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">When you use this product, you have to be very sincere in using the data of users. You can not publish the information of this WordPress plugin, and also, you can not use any data for personal usage. Overall, Learny LMS does not support any unethical content.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can not use any content on this platform that harms any region or nation. Also, you are not allowed to make any political discussion, personal promotion, or any kind of abusive words in this learning management system.</span></p>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(302, 371, '<h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Page settings</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In Learny LMS, an admin has the most privilege and responsibilities. As an admin, you can access the website page settings option. Here you can update the basic info about your website. For this, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in to the admin panel.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Learny LMS</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Plugin settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Page settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/navigating-page-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Navigating Page Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Page Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Navigating Page Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Page Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Page Settings</span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this settings panel, you have to provide the following information to configure the page setting.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set the login and registration page. (You can choose any option from the given option)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the student Dashboard page.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the Course player page.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set the Checkout page.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update page settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" button.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/updating-page-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Updating Page Settings Learny\" alt=\"Updating Page Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Page Settings Learny\" alt=\"Updating Page Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Updating Page Settings</span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">General Settings</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can update basic information about your WordPress website in the general settings option. For this, you have to follow the steps below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Learny LMS</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Plugin settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">General settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/navigating-general-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Navigating General Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating General Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Navigating General Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating General Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 3.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS General Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this settings panel, you have to provide the following information to configure the page setting.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set your business name.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide business email.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set business phone number.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set purchase code.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Upload system logo. (You can upload image logo from your device)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update general page settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option to save your data.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/updating-general-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Updating General Settings Learny\" alt=\"Updating General Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating General Settings Learny\" alt=\"Updating General Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 4.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Updating General Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Instructor Settings</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can configure instructor settings options from here. For this, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Learny LMS</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Plugin settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Instructor settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/navigating-instructor-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Navigating Instructor Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Instructor Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Navigating Instructor Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Instructor Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 5.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Instructor Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">In this settings panel, you have to provide the following information to configure the page setting.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Allow/Disallow the public instructor.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the instructor application note.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set the instructor revenue percentage.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set the admin revenue percentage.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"<b>Update Instructor Settings</b>\" option to save your data.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/updating-instructor-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Updating Instructor Settings Learny\" alt=\"Updating Instructor Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Instructor Settings Learny\" alt=\"Updating Instructor Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 6.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Updating Instructor Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">API Settings</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To support or run the different platforms in your plugin, you have to provide API (Application Programming Interface) keys. In this settings panel, you have to provide API keys. For this, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Learny LMS</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Plugin settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">API settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/navigating-api-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Navigating Api Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Api Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Navigating Api Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Api Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 7.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS API Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now you have to provide the information below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set the Youtube API key.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set the Vimeo API key.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update API Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"></span></p><p style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p><p></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/updating-api-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Updating Api Settings Learny\" alt=\"Updating Api Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Api Settings Learny\" alt=\"Updating Api Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 8.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Updating API Settings</span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Payment Settings</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can configure the payment settings from this settings option. Here, you can change, update the payment system of your application. For this, you have to follow the steps below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Learny LMS</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Plugin settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Payment settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/navigating-payment-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Navigating Payment Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Payment Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Navigating Payment Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Payment Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 9.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Payment Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, configure the system currency. You can set any currency you want. Here, you have to:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set a system currency</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set a currency position</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/system-currency-settings-learny.png\" title=\"System Currency Settings Learny\" alt=\"System Currency Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"System Currency Settings Learny\" alt=\"System Currency Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 10.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS System Currency Settings</span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Note:</em></strong><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;Make sure that your \"</em><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">System currency</em></strong><em style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" and other gateway currency are the same.</em></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><b>PayPal gateway:</b></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">After configuring the system currency settings, you have to configure the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">PayPal settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.\" For this, you have to:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set the activation status of PayPal.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the mode.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the client ID. (Sandbox)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set the secret key. (Sandbox)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Client ID. (Production)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Secret key. (Production)</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update Payment Settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option to save your data.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/updating-payment-settings.png\" title=\"Updating Payment Settings\" alt=\"Updating Payment Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Payment Settings\" alt=\"Updating Payment Settings\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 11.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Updating PayPal Settings</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To get the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Client ID</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" and \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Secret key</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" for your PayPal account, you have to follow the steps below:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Navigate to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">PayPal Developers Website</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" home page.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Login to the dashboard.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">You can also log in with your mobile number using&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">OTP</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Set up the profile.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Your Name</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Go to \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Dashboard</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" in the top right corner.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Create App</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" to create a new app.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Provide the details for the new app.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now you can see the PayPal Client Id and secret.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">WooCommerce Settings</span></h3><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">WooCommerce is the most popular e-commerce plugin. To configure this setting, you have to install this plugin to your WordPress. After that, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Learny LMS</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Choose the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Plugin settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">WooCommerce settings</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/navigating-woocommerce-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Navigating Woocommerce Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Woocommerce Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Navigating Woocommerce Settings Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Woocommerce Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 12.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS WooCommerce Settings-1</span></span></h5><h5><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span></span></h5><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Now, you can import your premium courses to the WooCommerce site as products. For this, you have to click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Synchronize Learny Courses</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">To import \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Completed</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" orders from WooCommerce, you have to click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Synchronize Learny Orders</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.&nbsp;</span></p><p></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"></p><p></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><br></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/woocommerce-settings-learny.png\" title=\"Woocommerce Settings Learny\" alt=\"Woocommerce Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Woocommerce Settings Learny\" alt=\"Woocommerce Settings Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 13.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS WooCommerce Settings-2&nbsp;</span></span></h5>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(303, 372, '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-size: 1.14844rem; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Create instructor account</span></h3><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">You can create an instructor\'s account manually or allow the public instructor to your website as an admin. If you allow the public instructor to your website, your students can apply to become an instructor. We will navigate you enrolling an instructor manually in this WordPress plugin.</span></p><ul style=\"padding-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Log in to the admin panel.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Select the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Learny LMS</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Click on the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Instructor</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Choose the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add new instructor</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" option.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/managing-users/navigating-add-new-instructor-learny.png\" title=\"Navigating Add New Instructor Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Add New Instructor Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Navigating Add New Instructor Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Add New Instructor Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p></h3><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Adding New Instructor</span></span></h5><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">After clicking on the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add new instructor</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" button, you have to provide information about your new instructor. They are:</span></p><ul style=\"padding-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Instructor\'s name</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Username</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Email</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Password</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Short bio</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Click on the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Submit</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" button to save your data.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/managing-users/submiting-new-instructor-learny.png\" title=\"Submiting New Instructor Learny\" alt=\"Submiting New Instructor Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Submiting New Instructor Learny\" alt=\"Submiting New Instructor Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p></h3><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Saving New Instructor\'s Info</span></span></h5><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></p></h3><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-size: 1.14844rem; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update &amp; Delete account</span></h3><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 0.875rem;\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can make an instructor enabled or disabled for using this site. You can also update and delete an instructor\'s account from the \"</span>Instructor<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\" option as an admin.&nbsp;For this, you have to follow the steps below:</span></span></p><ul style=\"padding-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Select the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Learny LMS</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Click on the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Instructor</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Here you can find the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Action</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" option. In this option, you can see the update and delete icons. To update the information, you have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"padding-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Select an instructor.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Click on the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" icon.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update required information.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Click on the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update User</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" button.&nbsp;</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/managing-users/updating-instructor-info-learny.png\" title=\"Updating Instructor Info Learny\" alt=\"Updating Instructor Info Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Instructor Info Learny\" alt=\"Updating Instructor Info Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p></h3><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); backgroun