pan data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update required information.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Click on the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Update User</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" button.&nbsp;</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/managing-users/updating-student-info-learny.png\" title=\"Updating Student Info Learny\" alt=\"Updating Student Info Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Updating Student Info Learny\" alt=\"Updating Student Info Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p></h3><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 6.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Student Info Updating Icon</span></span></h5><h3 style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-b