ottom: 0pt;\">Yes</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" button for confirmation.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background: transparent;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/managing-users/deleting-student-info-learny.png\" title=\"Deleting Student Info Learny\" alt=\"Deleting Student Info Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Deleting Student Info Learny\" alt=\"Deleting Student Info Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p></h3><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 7.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Student Deleting Icon</span></span></h5>', 1);
INSERT INTO `documentation` (`id`, `article_id`, `documentation`, `visibility`) VALUES
(305, 370, '<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">You can add extra plugins to your WordPress site to enhance the capability. The same goes with Learny LMS. You can add different kinds of third-party plugins to your WordPress. Like:</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-size: 1.14844rem; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">WooCommerce</span></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">WooCommerce is the most popular open-source e-commerce plugin for WordPress. This plugin is created for every kind of business. You can sell Learny LMS\'s premium courses through WooCommerce. You can also sync WooCommerce\'s completed orders to Learny.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">For this, you have to have WooCommerce on your WordPress site. If you do not have it, follow the instruction to install WooCommerce plugin.</span></p><ul style=\"padding-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(14, 16, 26);\"><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Go to your WordPress website.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Log in as Admin.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Select the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Plugins</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" option from the left menu.</span></li><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Choose the \"</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Add New</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\" option from the sub-menu.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/navigating-plugin-installation-learny.png\" title=\"Navigating Plugin Installation Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Plugin Installation Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Navigating Plugin Installation Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Plugin Installation Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Navigating Plugin Installation Learny\" alt=\"Navigating Plugin Installation Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 1.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Installing New Plugin</span></span></h5><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><ul style=\"padding-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent; color: rgb(14, 16, 26);\"><li style=\"color: rgb(30, 32, 34); max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Search for WooCommerce in the search bar.</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/creativeitem.com/uploads/documentation/learny-lms/getting-started-with-learny/search-bar-learny.png\" title=\"Search Bar Learny\" alt=\"Search Bar Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Search Bar Learny\" alt=\"Search Bar Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\"\" title=\"Search Bar Learny\" alt=\"Search Bar Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); max-width: 100%; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background: transparent;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></span></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); bac