(322, 400, '<p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Your students can add their favorite course to the wishlist. They can also update their wishlist if they want. To add a course to the wishlist, your students have to navigate:</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Log in as a student.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Select the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Learny Dashboard</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" from the top.</span></li><li style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Click on the \"</span><strong style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">My Wishlist</strong><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">\" option.&nbsp;</span></li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"><br></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt;\