Learny\" style=\"max-width : 100%;\" \"=\"\"></p><h5><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Figure 2.</span><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26); background: transparent; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learny LMS Deleting Course From Wishlist</span></span></h5>', 1);
